INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(101,'en','Jagras of the Ancient Forest','Slay 7 Jagras','Zorah Magdaros''s appearance has brought about changes in the local ecosystem. Head into Jagras territory to investigate, and take them out if necessary.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(102,'en','A Kestodon Kerfuffle','Complete the assignment','Zorah Magdaros''s appearance has driven a herd of Kestodon to new territory. We''ll need you to go out and thin that herd of head-butters.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(103,'en','The Great Jagras Hunt','Hunt a Great Jagras','Things I''m not interested in writing in my daily report: "Researchers swallowed whole by Great Jagras." Take it out before I actually have to write it!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(201,'en','Bird-Brained Bandit','Hunt a Kulu-Ya-Ku','The Kulu-Ya-Ku uses its dexterous forearms to carry objects. Left unchecked it''s liable to run off with crucial supplies. Step one of rebuilding a secure camp is hunting that thief!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(205,'en','Urgent: Pukei-Pukei Hunt','Hunt a Pukei-Pukei','That Pukei-Pukei is none too pleased to have that slag in its territory. It''ll be even less pleased if we send in our scholars to research it. Looks like we have to put it down.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(301,'en','The Best Kind of Quest','Complete the assignment','Something surely left by Zorah Magdaros was discovered out in the Wildspire Waste. Fifth Fleet hunters: Keep our scholars safe as you escort them out to investigate this new evidence.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(302,'en','Sinister Shadows in the Swamp','Complete the assignment','A young scholar has gotten separated from his escort out in the Wildspire Waste. Find him and escort him back to base. Neutralize any large monsters that pose a threat.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(305,'en','Flying Sparks: Tobi-Kadachi','Hunt a Tobi-Kadachi','Oh, my! That Tobi-Kadachi sure is getting in the way of progress! You hunters will never get a hold of these specialized tools I''m making if I become its dinner!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(306,'en','The Encroaching Anjanath','Hunt an Anjanath','As we''re gearing up to capture Zorah Magdaros, we need to secure Astera as much as we can. It''s too much of a risk to have that Anjanath roaming so close to base.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(401,'en','One for the History Books','Complete the assignment','At dawn we''ll attempt what no one in history has dared: Capture an elder dragon! Make your preparations and proceed to the site. May the Sapphire Star guide us all.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(405,'en','Ballooning Problems','Hunt a Paolumu','...I''m sorry, I just retched thinking about that monster''s face. Seriously, you''ll be doing it a favor...and us too. Hunt it and the Airship Engineer will have everything he needs.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(407,'en','Radobaan Roadblock','Hunt a Radobaan','The bones covering Radobaan''s body are gonna be tough to get through, but if we want to continue our survey of the Rotten Vale, you''ll need to find a way!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(408,'en','Legiana: Embodiment of Elegance','Hunt a Legiana','You already know how I feel about that intolerable creature. As long as it controls the skies in the highlands, we''ll never be able to make our descent. Do take care of it, won''t you?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(501,'en','Into the Bowels of the Vale','Complete the assignment','...... Certain death awaits you in the depths, but so does the key to finding Zorah Magdaros. A fair trade-off if you ask me.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(502,'en','A Fiery Throne Atop the Forest','Hunt a Rathalos','The First Wyverian''s not gonna spill the beans about Zorah until we stand on top of the food chain. That means we gotta hunt us a Rathalos! ...Does that mean we have to eat it too?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(503,'en','Horned Tyrant Below the Sands','Hunt a Diablos','The First Wyverian''s not gonna spill the beans about Zorah until we stand on top of the food chain. That means we gotta hunt us a Diablos! ...Does that mean we have to eat it too?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(504,'en','A Colossal Task','Complete the assignment','The operation is set to commence in the Everstream. Do everything you can to force Zorah Magdaros out to sea. We must not fail! May the Sapphire Star light our way!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(601,'en','Invader in the Waste','Hunt a Pukei-Pukei','A Pukei-Pukei in the Wildspire Waste!? As if that''s not already weird enough, this one''s extra tough. We''ve gotta get to the bottom of this! Be careful, Partner!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(605,'en','Tickled Pink','Hunt an Anjanath','A powerful Anjanath''s been sighted! Their kind''s the gold— pink?—standard for New World monsters. We can''t let this chance at an ideal sample slip away. Go hunt it ASAP!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(607,'en','Old World Monster in the New World','Complete the assignment','We''ve finally tracked down the source of those mysterious tracks. Report to the Coral Highlands and seek it out! I''ll be expecting your report as soon as you''re done!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(701,'en','A Wound and a Thirst','Slay Nergigante','The Nergigante''s long eyed us from the far side of the Elder Crossing, but now we have a lead on its whereabouts. If we can study it, it may reveal the Crossing''s true nature.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(801,'en','Kushala Daora, Dragon of Steel','Slay Kushala Daora','The elder dragon tracks in the forest? Kushala Daora. I''m sure of it. We know it''s in the Elder''s Recess. For the safety of everyone in Astera, we''re counting on you!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(802,'en','Teostra the Infernal','Slay Teostra','It''s Teostra that stalks the Waste—Emperor of flame. And now it sits in wait in the Elder''s Recess. Go to it, hunter, and end its searing reign!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(803,'en','Hellish Fiend Vaal Hazak','Slay Vaal Hazak','I''m absolutely positive that the effluvium is controlled by Vaal Hazak. Now to prove my theory once and for all. Go to the vale and seek out Vaal Hazak!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(804,'en','Land of Convergence','Complete the assignment','An immense energy flows through the New World, and we''ve found where it all leads to. Go with the Seeker and find out what''s there. May the Sapphire Star guide us all.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(805,'en','Beyond the Blasting Scales','Hunt two Bazelgeuse','This quest courts only those with absolute faith in their abilities. You face two abnormally powerful Bazelgeuse, Defeat them to prove you are a true master of the hunt!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(806,'en','Thunderous Rumble in the Highlands','Slay a Kirin','This quest seeks only those with an unquenchable flame in their chest. Make for the Coral Highlands and investigate the beast swathed in lightning. Beyond it lies true glory.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(241,'en','Learning the Clutch','Learn the mechanics of the clutch claw','The old man said that New World hunters need to keep innovating, and our latest innovation is the clutch claw, a new feature of the slinger. Time for you to get up to snuff on how to use it.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(151,'en','Butting Heads with Nature','Slay 12 Kestodon','Blasted Kestodon! Every single time we go out to collect samples, those annoying creatures knock us on our tushes! I wish they''d butt out of our research!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(152,'en','A Thicket of Thugs','Slay 7 Jagras','One of my field researchers wants to collect brightmoss to study. Only problem is, it''s mostly found in caves. Guess what else is mostly found in caves? That''s right...Jagras!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(153,'en','Fungal Flexin'' in the Ancient Forest','Deliver 20 Gourmet Shroomcaps','Supplements? At MY Canteen? Pfft! We''re all organic, baby! If you need vitamin D, get some Gourmet Shroomcaps! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(251,'en','The Great Glutton','Hunt a Great Jagras','I''m sure by now you''ve seen the way Great Jagras swallow its prey whole. One''s been spotted again in the forest. Take it out before one of my researchers gets gobbled up!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(252,'en','Camp Crasher','Hunt a Kulu-Ya-Ku','The other morning one of my researchers woke to his camp having been pilfered by one of those thieving Kulu-Ya-Ku. Do something about it before it ransacks another camp!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(261,'en','Snatch the Snatcher','Capture a Kulu-Ya-Ku','The Kulu-Ya-Ku uses its nimble forearms to pick up stones and eggs. Monsters that use tools are exceptionally rare. I''d like you to catch one for closer study.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(262,'en','The Pain from Gains','Slay 7 Gajau','My paw-thritis is acting up again. Years of Palico-ing will do that to you. The best remedy? Good ol'' Gajau liver oil! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(263,'en','Exterminator of the Waste','Slay 14 Vespoid','I need you to go out to the Wildspire Waste and waste a few Vespoids...or as I like to call them, punchin'' bags with wings. *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(351,'en','Scatternut Shortage','Hunt a Pukei-Pukei','A Pukei-Pukei must have shown up because it''s getting more and more difficult to gather scatternuts! We can''t study them if the only specimens we can gather are covered in poison!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(352,'en','The Current Situation','Hunt a Tobi-Kadachi','Don''t touch me! Don''t touch me! *zap* I told you NOT TO TOUCH ME! A blasted Tobi-Kadachi has shown up and now I can''t touch anything without getting— *ZAP* OUCH!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(361,'en','Mired in the Spire','Hunt a Barroth','The Carrier Ants out in the Wildspire Waste are extraordinary engineers. We''ve been trying to further our research of them but a Barroth appeared and mucked up our entire operation.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(362,'en','The Piscine Problem','Hunt a Jyuratodus','The Iron Helmcrab is such a fascinating creature. Just kick it over and out pops a piercing pod! We''d love to study them more but not with a Jyuratodus lurking about!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(363,'en','Prickly Predicament','Deliver 20 Bauble Cactuses','I''m confident the plants native to the waste will help us grow our Ancient Trees, but I need your help gathering them! *Unlocks a Botanical Research item on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(364,'en','Gettin'' Yolked in the Waste','Deliver 2 Herbivore Eggs','You ready for leg day!? GOOD! You''ll need ''em when you''re running from that Apceros herd! Now go get me my purr-otein! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(365,'en','Landing the Landslide Wyvern','Capture a Barroth','Barroth dwell in the marshes of the Wildspire Waste, but details of their activities, diet, and nesting habits remain unknown. Catch one to help shed light on the issue.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(331,'en','Special Arena: Pukei-Pukei','Hunt a Pukei-Pukei','A new challenger: Pukei-Pukei, the Toxic Tussler, the Lickin'' Machine! He won''t listen when you say "no tongues"! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(332,'en','Special Arena: Barroth','Hunt a Barroth','A new challenger: Barroth, the Hulking Headbutt, the Skull-cracker! Lose to this guy, and your name is mud! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(333,'en','Special Arena: Tobi-Kadachi','Hunt a Tobi-Kadachi','A new challenger: Tobi-Kadachi, the Leaping Lizard, the Bite-master! He''ll clean your clock with thunder shocks! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(451,'en','One Helluva Sinus Infection','Hunt an Anjanath','Our entire department is out with the flu because of that Anjanath. How could they not be? The Ancient Forest is covered from top to bottom with that nasty mucus!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(452,'en','Gettin'' Yolked in the Forest','Deliver 2 Wyvern Eggs','You ready for leg day!? GOOD! You''ll need ''em when you''re running from that Rathian! Now go get me my purr-otein! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(461,'en','Royal Relocation','Hunt a Rathian','The samples I need to further my Ancient Tree research are right under a Rathian''s nest. Perhaps you can move it for me? *Unlocks a Botanical Research item on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(471,'en','It''s a Crying Shamos','Slay 11 Shamos','I almost feel bad for ''em. Those scrawny little monsters don''t even stand a chance. Go flex on ''em while I get the goods! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(472,'en','A Tzitzi for Science','Hunt a Tzitzi-Ya-Ku','We''ve heard talk of the Coral Highlands'' Tzitzi-Ya-Ku, how it emits flashes of light to blind its enemies. We must know the mechanics involved. Field team, please hunt one for our studies!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(473,'en','Sorry You''re Not Invited','Hunt a Paolumu','This is sort of an odd request but there is a birthday party coming up this weekend and we''re in desperate need of balloons. If you could help us out you''d be a real hero!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(474,'en','What a Bunch of Abalone','Deliver 10 Super Abalone','You ready for arms day!? GOOD! You''re gonna need ''em to gather these ingredients I''ve had my eye on! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(475,'en','White Monster for a White Coat','Capture a Paolumu','Paolumu dwell in the Coral Highlands, but details of their activities, diet, and nesting habits remain unknown. Catch one to help shed light on this mysterious creature.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(481,'en','Persistent Pests','Slay 14 Hornetaur','There''s a spot that I''m certain hides the secret to new Ancient Tree growth but it''s infested with Hornetaurs! *Unlocks a Botanical Research slot on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(482,'en','A Rotten Thing To Do','Hunt a Great Girros','I was work-k-king the Rotten V-Vale when a G-G-Great Girros z-z-zapped me from behind. I g-got out in one piece, but I''m still all t-t-tingly... Finish the j-j-job for me? P-Please!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(483,'en','A Bone to Pick','Hunt a Radobaan','It''s nearly impossible for any of our researchers to study fossils in the Rotten Vale because they keep getting stuck to that blasted Radobaan rolling around down there...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(484,'en','On Nightmare''s Wings','Slay 5 Raphinos','Here at the Second Fleet, we''ve been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We''re counting on you to take this quest!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(5003,'en','Troubled Troupers','Hunt 2 Tzitzi-Ya-Ku','"We Troupers are getting batterfanged by two Tzitzi-Ya-Ku. Please har-meow-nize with our warriors to wallop them into hightailing it!" (Translation by the Lynian Researcher)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(431,'en','Special Arena: Anjanath','Hunt an Anjanath','A new challenger: Anjanath, the Jaws of Death, the Stomp-asaurus! He''s just stopped by for a quick bite! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(432,'en','Special Arena: Rathian','Hunt a Rathian','A new challenger: Rathian, the Queen o'' Green, the Sky-borne Slasher! Don''t get the lady angry; she''s poison! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(433,'en','Special Arena: Paolumu','Hunt a Paolumu','A new challenger: Paolumu, the Punishing Puffball, the Fear-igible! It may not be fair, but he''s walking on air! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(434,'en','Special Arena: Radobaan','Hunt a Radobaan','A new challenger: Radobaan, the Roto-Ravager, the Grinder! Better dodge fast, or you''ll be boned! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(551,'en','When Desire Becomes an Obsession','Hunt a Rathalos','They say that Rathalos possess the rarest of gems, but I''m having a hard to time obtaining one. I''ve already gone through ten or so of them with no luck. Oh well, bring me another!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(552,'en','Redefining the "Power Couple"','Hunt all target monsters','Here at the Second Fleet, we''ve been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We''re counting on you to take this quest!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(561,'en','Twin Spires Upon the Sands','Hunt a Diablos','Did you know there''s a species of insect that survives by burrowing into Diablos tails? No? Well neither do we! And we won''t find out unless you go and bring us one to be sure!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(571,'en','A Humid Headache','Hunt a Legiana','This weather is so humid you could cut the air with a great sword! Our department could do with some climate control and I know just the monster that can provide some relief!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(572,'en','Gone in a Flash','Slay a Kirin','Why are you still here? An elder dragon''s been spotted and you''re just hanging out!? Hurry up before it gets away! *Unlocks a new Specialized Tool on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(581,'en','Scratching the Itch','Hunt an Odogaron','This morning I awoke to a brilliant epiphany! I have an idea for something every hunter needs after a long day out in the field...Odogaron backscratchers!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(582,'en','Man''s Best Fiend','Capture an Odogaron','I really miss my old pet. The days we spent going to the park, playing fetch. I long for that companionship... that loyalty. Please go out and find me a new one.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(583,'en','The Meat of the Matter','Deliver 2 Lumps of Meat','You ready for back day!? GOOD! You''ll need to put your back into it to get all the ingredients on this list! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(531,'en','Special Arena: Legiana','Hunt a Legiana','A new challenger: Legiana, the Slipstream Striker, the Wing leader! Remember, you can''t spell flight without fight! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(532,'en','Special Arena: Odogaron','Hunt an Odogaron','A new challenger: Odogaron, the Muscle Mutt, the Rex Who Wrecks! He''ll bite your leg to fetch the stick inside! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(533,'en','Special Arena: Rathalos','Hunt a Rathalos','A new challenger: Rathalos, the Red-Hot Raider, the Fire-starter! Forgive the fireballs; he likes his meals cooked! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(534,'en','Special Arena: Diablos','Hunt a Diablos','A new challenger: Diablos, the Sandy Stampede, Biggus Diggus! Don''t hang around if he''s underground! Think you can go toe-to-toe—er, toe-to-claw with this heavy hitter!?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(641,'en','Left Quite the Impression','Guide Zorah Magdaros','Doesn''t the sight of Zorah Magdaros make your heart skip a beat? Let me assure you, seeing its scales close up is just as awe-inspiring. It''s imperative that we study it more.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(651,'en','Hard to Swallow','Hunt a Great Jagras','We''ve gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Great Jagras appearing in the Ancient Forest. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its gluttonous appetite!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(652,'en','Googly-eyed Green Monster','Hunt a Pukei-Pukei','We''ve gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Pukei-Pukei appearing in the Ancient Forest. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its poisonous attacks!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(653,'en','A Hair-Raising Experience','Hunt a Tobi-Kadachi','We''ve gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Tobi-Kadachi appearing in the Ancient Forest. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its lightning speed!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(654,'en','It Can''t See You if You Don''t Move','Hunt an Anjanath','We''ve gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Anjanath appearing in the Ancient Forest. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its fiery attacks!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(655,'en','The Sleeping Sylvan Queen','Hunt a Rathian','A major change in the ecosystem is driving monsters from their natural habitats. Head to the Ancient Forest and begin your investigation of the invading Rathian immediately!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(656,'en','Stuck in Their Ways','Capture a Tobi-Kadachi','Those three crazy old scholars went to study a LIVE Tobi-Kadachi. Please go capture it before they hurt themselves! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(661,'en','Keep Your Hands to Yourself!','Hunt a Kulu-Ya-Ku','We''ve gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Kulu-Ya-Ku roaming the Wildspire Waste. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its clever attacks!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(662,'en','A Crown of Mud and Anger','Hunt a Barroth','We''ve gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Barroth roaming the Wildspire Waste. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its mud-caked attacks!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(663,'en','Pukei-Pukei Ambush','Hunt a Pukei-Pukei','A major change in the ecosystem is driving monsters from their natural habitats. Head to the Wildspire Waste and begin your investigation of the invading Pukei-Pukei ASAP!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(665,'en','Up to Your Waist in the Waste','Hunt a Jyuratodus','We''ve gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Jyuratodus appearing in the Wildspire Waste. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware of getting stuck in the muck!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(666,'en','Brown Desert, Green Queen','Hunt a Rathian','We''ve gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Rathian appearing in the Wildspire Waste. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware of its poisonous tail!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(667,'en','Trespassing Troublemaker','Hunt an Anjanath','A major change in the ecosystem is driving monsters from their natural habitats. Head to the Wildspire Waste and begin your investigation of the invading Anjanath ASAP!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(671,'en','Say Cheese!','Hunt a Tzitzi-Ya-Ku','We''ve gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Tzitzi-Ya-Ku appearing in the Coral Highlands. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its blinding flash attacks!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(672,'en','Loop the Paolumu','Hunt a Paolumu','We''ve gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Paolumu appearing in the Coral Highlands. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware of its airburst attacks!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(681,'en','A Tingling Taste','Hunt a Great Girros','...... Why do I want you to hunt a Great Girros? Well, I''ll tell you later. I know, how devilish of me. Run along now...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(682,'en','Stuck in a Rut','Hunt a Radobaan','We''ve gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Radobaan appearing in the Rotten Vale. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware of its rolling attacks!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(683,'en','Chef Quest! Pumped to Deliver','Deliver 4 Forgotten Fossils','Now that you''ve worked both your upper and lower body, are you ready to put it to good use!? GOOD! Let''s Work! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(684,'en','Chef Quest! A Rotten Request','Slay 10 Girros','These little monsters think you''re playing with them! Show ''em what you''re made of! Let''s say... 10 reps? *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(691,'en','A Meow for Help','Slay 13 Gastodon','Every time I try to gather something for my meowster out in the Everstream, these Gastodon knock me on my tail! MEOW-CH! Can you lend a Felyne a paw here?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(692,'en','A Scalding Scoop','Slay 5 Barnos','I was out on assignment when a Barnos barfed something at me. Whatever it was it was HOT, painfully hot! But also the sells-lots-of-copies kind of hot! Help me get my story!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(693,'en','Dodogama Drama','Hunt a Dodogama','Hey, we''ve gotten a report of an unusually fine monster specimen roaming around. We need to seize on this opportunity, so we need you to investigate ASAP!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(694,'en','Chef Quest! Gajalaka Lockdown','Defeat 10 Gajalaka','Meow my god! Are these lil'' guys tryin'' to flex on you? Show ''em what you''re packin''! Let''s say... 10 reps! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(631,'en','Special Arena: HR Pukei-Pukei','Hunt a Pukei-Pukei','A new challenger: Pukei-Pukei, the Toxic Tussler, the Lickin'' Machine! He won''t listen when you say "no tongues"! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(632,'en','Special Arena: HR Barroth','Hunt a Barroth','A new challenger: Barroth, the Hulking Headbutt, the Skullcracker! Lose to this guy, and your name is mud! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(633,'en','Special Arena: HR Tobi-Kadachi','Hunt a Tobi-Kadachi','A new challenger: Tobi-Kadachi, the Leaping Lizard, the Bitemaster! He''ll clean your clock with thunder shocks! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(634,'en','Special Arena: HR Anjanath','Hunt an Anjanath','A new challenger: Anjanath, the Jaws of Death, the Stompasaurus! He''s just stopped by for a quick bite! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(635,'en','Special Arena: HR Rathian','Hunt a Rathian','A new challenger: Rathian, the Queen o'' Green, the Skyborne Slasher! Don''t get the lady angry; she''s poison! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(636,'en','Special Arena: HR Paolumu','Hunt a Paolumu','A new challenger: Paolumu, the Punishing Puffball, the Fearigible! It may not be fair, but he''s walking on air! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(637,'en','Special Arena: HR Radobaan','Hunt a Radobaan','A new challenger: Radobaan, the Roto-Ravager, the Grinder! Better dodge fast, or you''ll be boned! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(751,'en','Rathalos Rematch','Hunt a Rathalos','We''ve gotten a disturbing report of another unusually powerful Rathalos in the Ancient Forest. Let that red beast know who REALLY stands atop the food chain here!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(752,'en','Rathalos in Blue','Hunt an Azure Rathalos','The field team has spotted an Azure Rathalos patroling the skies. Subspecies like these are highly valuable to the Commission''s research efforts. Get going, hunter!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(753,'en','The Red and Blue Crew','Hunt all target monsters','Here at the Second Fleet, we''ve been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We''re counting on you to take this quest!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(761,'en','Pretty In Pink','Hunt a Pink Rathian','The field team has spotted a Pink Rathian stalking the local wildlife. Subspecies like these are highly valuable to the Commission''s research efforts. Get going, hunter!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(762,'en','Well, That Diablos!','Hunt a Diablos','We''ve gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Diablos appearing in the Wildspire Waste. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware of its charging attacks!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(763,'en','Two-horned Hostility','Hunt a Black Diablos','Hey, we''ve gotten a report of an unusually fine monster specimen roaming around. We need to seize on this opportunity, so we need you to investigate ASAP!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(764,'en','RRRRRumble in the Waste!','Hunt all target monsters','*sigh* I''ve already told you what I want you to do. Run along now and complete this quest if you want your new toy. *Unlocks a new Specialized Tool on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(771,'en','A Cherry Wind upon the Reefs','Hunt a Pink Rathian','The field team has spotted a Pink Rathian stalking the local wildlife. Subspecies like these are highly valuable to the Commission''s research efforts. Get going, hunter!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(772,'en','Legiana: Highlands Royalty','Hunt a Legiana','We''ve gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Legiana appearing in the Coral Highlands. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware its swift and icy attacks!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(773,'en','A Sore Site','Hunt an Odogaron','Ugh! Every time I go out to the highlands to observe my beloved Paolumu, that gnarly monster is there! Please do something! *Unlocks a new Canteen ingredient on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(774,'en','Talons of Ire and Ice','Hunt all target monsters','There''s a spot I''m certain hides the secret to growing Ancient Trees. Unfortunately, two nasty monsters are patrolling that area. *Unlocks a Botanical Research slot on first time completion.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(781,'en','Odogaron Unleashed','Hunt an Odogaron','We''ve gotten a disturbing report of an unusually powerful Odogaron appearing in the Rotten Vale. Begin your investigation ASAP, but beware of its powerful claws!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(791,'en','Lavasioth, Monster of Magma','Hunt a Lavasioth','Hey, we''ve gotten a report of an unusually fine monster specimen roaming around. We need to seize on this opportunity, so we need you to investigate ASAP!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(792,'en','Ore-eating Occupier','Hunt an Uragaan','We''ve gotten a report of an unusually fine monster specimen roaming around. We need to seize on this opportunity, so we need you to investigate ASAP!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(793,'en','Ruler of the Azure Skies','Hunt an Azure Rathalos','The field team has spotted an Azure Rathalos patroling the skies. Subspecies like these are highly valuable to the Commission''s research efforts. Get going, hunter!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(794,'en','Bazelgeuse in the Field of Fire','Hunt a Bazelgeuse','That eccentric trio has gone and done it again! Now that they''ve discovered the location of a Bazelgeuse, they''re off to study it! Please hunt it before they get themselves hurt!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(795,'en','A Fiery Convergence','Hunt all target monsters','Here at the Second Fleet, we''ve been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We''re counting on you to take this quest!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(738,'en','Special Arena: HR Black Diablos','Hunt a Black Diablos','A new challenger: Black Diablos, the Dark Destroyer, the Horn Express! Run, don''t walk, from this furious fiend! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(731,'en','Special Arena: HR Pink Rathian','Hunt a Pink Rathian','A new challenger: Pink Rathian, the Burning Blossom, the Beauty Who Bites! Best not stop to smell the roses! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(732,'en','Special Arena: HR Legiana','Hunt a Legiana','A new challenger: Legiana, the Slipstream Striker, the Wingleader! Remember, you can''t spell flight without fight! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(733,'en','Special Arena: HR Odogaron','Hunt an Odogaron','A new challenger: Odogaron, the Muscle Mutt, the Rex Who Wrecks! He''ll bite your leg to fetch the stick inside! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(734,'en','Special Arena: HR Uragaan','Hunt an Uragaan','A new challenger: Uragaan, the Rolling Rocket, the Chinstigator! Once he starts spinning, uragoner! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(735,'en','Special Arena: HR Rathalos','Hunt a Rathalos','A new challenger: Rathalos, the Red-Hot Raider, the Firestarter! Forgive the fireballs; he likes his meals cooked! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(736,'en','Special Arena: HR Azure Rathalos','Hunt an Azure Rathalos','A new challenger: Azure Rathalos, the Sapphire Sultan, the True Blue Terror! Bow down to the king of all wyverns! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(737,'en','Special Arena: HR Diablos','Hunt a Diablos','A new challenger: Diablos, the Sandy Stampede, Biggus Diggus! Don''t hang around if he''s underground! The gloves are off—not that we have gloves that big...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(50751,'en','Today''s Special: Hunter Flambé','Hunt a Deviljho','Partner, we''re part of the food chain too if you think about it. And that''s bad news for us if a Deviljho gets a hankering for a hunter burger! So, let''s hunt it down before we''re lunch!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(851,'en','A Portent of Disaster','Slay a Kushala Daora','Here at the Second Fleet, we''ve been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We''re counting on you to take this quest!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(893,'en','Hellfire''s Stronghold','Slay a Teostra','Teostra. Just saying the name makes my quill tip quiver. Some believe it''s bad luck to cut the fur from this regal beast, but for the sake of the future, we must study it!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(895,'en','The Winds of Wrath Bite Deep','Slay a Kushala Daora','We''ve got a Kushala Daora running ''round, tearin'' things up. Seems like it was kicked out of its territory. Question is, what did the kickin''? Time to investigate!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(861,'en','A Blaze on the Sand','Slay a Teostra','Here at the Second Fleet, we''ve been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We''re counting on you to take this quest!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(871,'en','Lightning Strikes Twice','Slay a Kirin','Yet another Kirin has shown up and you''re just here, playing with your Palico!? We might never get this chance again to study it! Go go GOOOOOO!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(881,'en','Stirrings from the Grave','Slay a Vaal Hazak','Vaal Hazak serves its purpose in the life cycle of the New World, but now that it has stirred from its nest of decay, it threatens to ruin the whole ecosystem. It must be stopped!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(894,'en','The Eater of Elders','Slay Nergigante','Nergigante is one helluva beast, and still so much we don''t know ''bout it. Which is why I need you! If we''re lucky, we might get to see two elder dragons squaring off!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(891,'en','The Eater of Elders','Slay Nergigante','Nergigante is one helluva beast, and still so much we don''t know ''bout it. Which is why I need you! If we''re lucky, we might get to see two elder dragons squaring off!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(892,'en','Master of the Gale','Slay a Kushala Daora','Did you know that some cultures worship Kushala Daora as a god of wind? Luckily, we''re not one of them! I''m determined to study its mastery of flight...just think of the benefits!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(896,'en','The Fires of Hell Bite Deep','Slay a Teostra','We''ve got a riled up Teostra on the warpath. Seems like it was kicked out of its kingdom. Question is, what did the kickin''? Time to investigate!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(50891,'en','Blue Prominence','Slay Lunastra','I was out studying the feeding habits of some seriously cute local fauna when—WOWZERS—a gigantic blue elder dragon appears! Take care of it so I can get back to research that matters!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(50892,'en','Blue Prominence','Slay Lunastra','I was out studying the feeding habits of some seriously cute local fauna when—WOWZERS—a gigantic blue elder dragon appears! Take care of it so I can get back to research that matters!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(50861,'en','Infernal Monarchy','Slay all target monsters','I don''t know how it happened, but we have the chance to observe Teostra and Lunastra behavior in the Wildspire Waste! This is something we can''t miss! Go see for yourself, but don''t get hurt!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(992,'en','The White Winds of the New World','Hunt all target monsters','To the hunter who has conquered every investigation, I offer this, the ultimate quest. Enter the Special Arena and take on the New World. Use all that lies before you, and claim glory.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(991,'en','A Light Upon the River''s Gloom','Slay Xeno''jiiva','Xeno''jiiva is such a marvelous, mysterious example of exotic monster biology. We could study it for a hundred years if we just had enough samples! That''s your cue, Hunter.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(995,'en','The Sapphire Star''s Guidance','Slay all target monsters','To the unparalleled hunter, I offer this final quest. Return to the Elder''s Recess and brave the elders'' onslaught. Use all within your grasp to prove yourself master of the New World.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(996,'en','Showdown: the Muck and the Maul','Hunt all target monsters','Here at the Second Fleet, we''ve been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We''re counting on you to take this quest!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(997,'en','New World Sky, New World Flower','Hunt all target monsters','Here at the Second Fleet, we''ve been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We''re counting on you to take this quest!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(998,'en','A Summons from Below','Hunt all target monsters','Here at the Second Fleet, we''ve been working to develop new tools to help your hunts, but we need YOUR help gathering the materials. We''re counting on you to take this quest!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(961,'en','Beyond the Blasting Scales','Hunt 2 Bazelgeuse','This quest courts only those with absolute faith in their abilities. You face two abnormally powerful Bazelgeuse, Defeat them to prove you are a true master of the hunt!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(971,'en','Thunderous Rumble in the Highlands','Slay a Kirin','This quest seeks only those with an unquenchable flame in their chest. Make for the Coral Highlands and investigate the beast swathed in lightning. Beyond it lies true glory.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(50991,'en','A Visitor from Eorzea','Slay the Behemoth','A Behemoth has appeared in the Elder''s Recess. Conventional methods won''t work, call upon other trustworthy hunte— adventurers to help quell the beast!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(50701,'en','The Food Chain Dominator','Hunt a Deviljho','The Deviljho is a frightening presence that takes the idea of the food chain and crushes it between its massive jaws! Now it''s here in the New World. It''s time to get investigating!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(50801,'en','The Blazing Sun','Slay Teostra','A team has spotted Teostra in the Wildspire Waste. I say it''s an opportune time to go and have an audience with the infernal emperor, wouldn''t you say?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(50802,'en','Pandora''s Arena','Complete the assignment','There''s a saying about a cornered animal that slips me mind— Either way, there''s wounded Teostra corralled in the Special Arena. Something''s up with it. Go and check it out, eh?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(50803,'en','No Remorse, No Surrender','Slay all target monsters','I never thought I''d live to see both the emperor and his empress in one spot. It''s only fitting that you have the honor of ending their reign.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(50601,'en','A Visitor from Another World','Complete the assignment','My weirdo partner won''t shut up about some non-animal animal he found in the Wildspire Waste. Do you wanna tag along? Whatever it is, it''s bound to be something interesting!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(50905,'en','The Legendary Beast','Complete the assignment','Some kind of beast has arrived in the New World due to the instability of the aether. We have to do something otherwise every living thing in the New World is in serious danger!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(50906,'en','He Taketh It with His Eyes','Slay the Behemoth','It was a Behemoth, an Eorzean beast, in the Elder''s Recess. Heed the moogle''s advice, call upon other trustworthy hunte— adventurers to help quell this terror!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(50910,'en','Contract: Trouble in the Ancient Forest','Complete the assignment','Attention field team! An anomaly has been discovered in the Ancient Forest. Help the witcher resolve this issue. <STYL MOJI_RED_DEFAULT>In this quest, you will get to play as Geralt of Rivia.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(50902,'en','The Fury of El Dorado','Repel Kulve Taroth','The old girl is back and stronger than ever, this time dressed to the nines in a glittering white gold coat! With the First and Fifth working together, we won''t let this golden opportunity go to waste!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61605,'en','Mosswinin'' and Dinin''','Slay 5 Mosswine','The Admiral and Meowscular Chef trapped some Mosswine and put them into the Arena. I didn''t have the courage to tell them, but those Mosswine look purr-ty odd to me. Take a look!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61103,'en','Where Sun Meets Moon','Hunt all target monsters','I heard there''s a period of time when diurnal and nocturnal endemic life meet, so I wanted to see for myself, but now I''m in a jam! (Special ticket and increased rare material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61104,'en','Timberland Troublemakers','Hunt 2 Anjanath','I woke up early to go and fetch some Goldbloom, but I found a grumpy Anjanath standing in my way! Take care of him, will ya? (Rare material reward chance up, special ticket available)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61105,'en','Every Hunter''s Dream','Hunt all target monsters','A hunter came by with a blueprint of a weapon he wanted. I still have the prints lying around, so if you want one of your own, get me the materials and I''ll start workin''.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61601,'en','Midnight Mayhem','Slay 10 Gastodon','"The heck, am I lost? I don''t recognize this place. Oh well, I might as well have some fun while I''m here!" (Translation by the Lynian Researcher) (Special ticket rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61603,'en','A Royal Pain','Hunt all target monsters','I wouldn''t mind going home, but I hate all the royal hubbub that goes with it. Fiver, remind me why I joined the Fifth. (Special ticket and increased rare material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61604,'en','Kings Know No Fear','Hunt all target monsters','Just looking at a Rathalos reminds me of how irrelevant I am compared to the King of the Skies. And I hate it! Help me be famous too! (Increased chance of rare material rewards, special ticket available)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61606,'en','The Greatest Jagras','Hunt a Great Jagras','So I heard that a hunter had a Great Jagras cornered, but when they went to finish it off, a shadow appeared. What do you think it is? Heh, go out and find out for yourself! (Special ticket rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61607,'en','The Name''s Lavasioth!','Hunt a Lavasioth','Yo, we got asked to research a monster that no one ever wants to research! You know the one, that big floppy fishy that likes to lounge around in the lava! Yeah, THAT one! (Special ticket rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67105,'en','USJ: Gold Star Treatment','Hunt 3 Great Jagras','USJ is pleased to bring you the most exciting attraction ever! Witness this grand world in all of its golden glory! You''ll be presented with some fantastic equipment once you''re done!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67821,'en','Old Dog, New Trick','Hunt a Frostfang Barioth','What a proud figure I must make, sitting here with my arms crossed. But perhaps I should learn the ways of the new generation, starting with the clutch claw? I heard a Gold Melding Ticket would be the prize, heh.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67103,'en','A Rush of Blood','Hunt 2 Odogaron','Oh no! There''s this big ol'' monster that looks a lot like our Rush! Someone''s gotta calm the big boy down! Help us out, and we''ll give you some special gear for your Palico!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67603,'en','USJ Blazing Azure Stars!','Hunt all target monsters','USJ is pleased to present the most EXPLOSIVE show ever! Our twin blue stars will show you a dance like you''ve never seen before! Complete our challenge, and earn some fantastic armor!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67605,'en','Code: Red','Hunt all target monsters','Legends say in a far off land, a demon hunter in a red coat offed demons with a sickeningly sweet style. How about we make a legend out of you too? If you''re interested, jump in.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67608,'en','SDF: Silent, Deadly, and Fierce','Hunt all target monsters','Had an interestin'' fella in a white robe board me ship, looking for passage to the New World. Gave me quite a unique gift as a fee. I bet you can craft something real nice with it. If you can take care of this quest for me, it''s all yours!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67606,'en','A Visitor from Eorzea (Extreme)','Slay a Behemoth','Another Behemoth has appeared in the Elder''s Recess and is even more dangerous than the last! Summon other adventurers and quell the beast! <STYL MOJI_RED_DEFAULT>(Extremely difficult! Rewards: Drachen layered armor and guild card title)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67610,'en','Contract: Woodland Spirit','Slay the Ancient Leshen','A portal appeared in the Ancient Forest, and a strange creature came through it. The beast is called a woodland spirit and it''s extremely dangerous. <STYL MOJI_RED_DEFAULT>Quest level close to Death March! difficulty in The Witcher 3.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66101,'en','Chew The Fat','Hunt 2 Great Jagras','Yo, got a quest for you, but don''t worry, this is right up your alley. We got a couple of Great Jagras that need to be taken care of. Trust me, the rewards will be worth it.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66102,'en','Ya-Ku With That?','Hunt all target monsters','Hunter, these two meownsters are su-purr good at stealing eggs and dropping wingdrakes in a flash. But purrhaps they''ll make for good equipment too, mew get me?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66106,'en','Greeting the Gluttons','Hunt all target monsters','Huh? Yeah, this is a quest from the Meowscular Chef. Whoa, you''ll go instead of me? Wow, thanks a bunch! To show my gratitude, the next meal''s on me!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(64101,'en','Wicked Wildspire Warfare','Hunt all target monsters','Do you know what''ll happen if we get a couple of highly territorial monsters in one spot? No? Neither do I! Let''s find out. Come out on top to earn Armor Spheres!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66103,'en','Flesh Cleaved to Bone','Hunt all target monsters','So...let me get this straight, you''re going to step into the arena and get between Fido and its chew toy? Teaching it to play dead, are we?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66104,'en','Kirin The Myth','Slay 2 Kirin','I looked left, it appeared on the right. I glanced behind me, it showed up in front of me. When I thought there was one of them, there were two. I''m outmatched here. This task is all yours.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66105,'en','The Poison Posse','Hunt all target monsters','They say the most beautiful of chalices are poisonous. But I don''t think that applies to flying wyverns. But just in case, look into that for me.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(62608,'en','Gaze Upon the Dawn','Guide Zorah Magdaros','Whenever I see Zorah Magdaros, I can''t help but feel sad, and a bit homesick. Let''s finish up our research so I can go back to the Old World and meet my master and former teammates again!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(65601,'en','Scrapping with the Shamos','Hunt 13 Shamos','I''m getting bombarded with requests left n'' right for the stuff I''m wearing, but I''m gonna need some special materials to meet demand. That''s your cue, Hunter. You know what to do.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(65602,'en','A Flash in the Pan','Hunt 3 Tzitzi-Ya-Ku','My dear sister and I were suffering from poor eyesight, but the Second Fleet Master crafted us some fine spectacles. I''ll give mine to you if you help me test them out!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(65603,'en','Egg Lovers United','Hunt a Kulu-Ya-Ku','While out gathering egg specimens, a familiar shadow took me unawares. But I believe we can use this for our own purposes! Study the Kulu-Ya-Ku''s behavioral patterns, and report back!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(65604,'en','Wiggle Me This','Deliver 10 Wigglers','Wha--hey, don''t throw that net on me, I''m not a Wiggler! Fooled you, eh? If you want something like what I''m wearing, then you''ll have to help me with my research!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(65605,'en','Triple Threat Throwdown','Hunt all target monsters','This is a quest that I''ve prepared...just for you. You won''t believe how many decorations you''ll get if you can complete this quest! Now, show me what you got!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(64601,'en','Rollin'' With The Uragaan','Hunt 2 Uragaan','Urk, my head is still spinning from what I just saw. We need someone to take out these troublemakers before anyone else gets queasy. Complete this quest for a lot of Armor Spheres!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66601,'en','Deep Green Blues','Hunt all target monsters','The monsters lurking deep in the Ancient Forest seem intent on facing off with each other. This could be a huge boon for our research. Hunters, don''t let this opportunity pass us by!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66602,'en','Wildspire Bolero','Hunt all target monsters','The monsters roaming the Wildspire Waste seem intent on facing off with each other. This could be a huge boon for our research. Hunters, don''t let this opportunity pass us by!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66603,'en','Coral Waltz','Hunt all target monsters','The monsters roaming the Coral Highlands seem intent on facing off with each other. This could be a huge boon for our research. Hunters, don''t let this opportunity pass us by!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66604,'en','Effluvial Opera','Hunt all target monsters','The monsters roaming the Rotten Vale seem intent on facing off with each other. This could be a huge boon for our research. Hunters, don''t let this opportunity pass us by!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66605,'en','Rock N'' Roll Recess','Hunt all target monsters','The monsters roaming the Elder''s Recess seem intent on facing off with each other. This could be a huge boon for our research. Hunters, don''t let this opportunity pass us by!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66606,'en','This is How Revolts Start','Hunt all target monsters','This is preposterous! Why can''t I gather Kingly Cactus in peace!? This is beyond annoying, it''s an uprising I tell you! Go out there and see for yourself');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(62502,'en','The Deathly Quiet Curtain','Slay Vaal Hazak','The truly horrifying things are the ones sleeping in silence, no? But what could it be? The Third Fleet urges you to press on, to lift the curtain off of this mystery and feed our obsession.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(62503,'en','A Whisper of White Mane','Slay Kirin','At first I thought it was an illusion, staring down at me. That white mist gave me chills I''ll never forget. I need your help to confirm my findings.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(62504,'en','The Scorn of the Sun','Slay Teostra','When I first fought a Teostra back in the Old World, my fear washed over me, but it gave me the fire to fight. But now I realized it''s calmness, not fear, that you need to slay it.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(62505,'en','The Eye of the Storm','Slay Kushala Daora','Kushala''s existence reminds us of how great and fearful nature is. But it also reminds us of those who stood up against the beast. Stand tall hunter, and return the skies to blue.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(62506,'en','The Heralds of Destruction Cry','Slay Nergigante','I still remember when that thing showed up. I heard horns blaring in my head. It sounded like a song of destruction. I need help with my research, so those horns can stop!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(62511,'en','When Blue Dust Surpasses Red Lust','Slay Lunastra','What is TRUE love? *sigh* One must witness the passionate bond between the empress and emperor of flame to truly know. Get too close and surely you''ll get burned. Like I did...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(62515,'en','Relish the Moment','Hunt a Deviljho','We''ve discovered an insanely fierce Deviljho! It seems the cause of his bad mood is his diet of Streamstones. Quell the beast, and take those Streamstones for yourself!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(62606,'en','Undying Alpenglow','Guide Zorah Magdaros','My home was in the path of Zorah Magdaros, and the result was tragic. Now I''m with the Fifth, and I need your help to make sure our operation is a success! I must avenge my hometown!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(62607,'en','Like a Moth to the Flame','Slay Xeno''jiiva','Once more, I want to see that source of energy. The one born of light that has beckoned us all here to the New World. Let us embark on this journey once again if you are ready.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(62609,'en','Keeper of the Otherworld','Slay Xeno''jiiva','During my research, I came across a river. Just as I was about to swim across, I spotted some kind of supernatural light. Its existence defied all explanation. Help me unravel this mystery.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(65606,'en','A Simple Task','Deliver 10 Gourmet Shroomcap','While gathering samples out in the field, I noticed a number of rare tracks. I need a capable hunter to investigate these tracks, plus gather the rest of my samples!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(65607,'en','Tracking the Delivery','Deliver 10 Blue Beryl','While gathering samples out in the field, I noticed a number of rare tracks. I''ll need a capable hunter to get the remainder of my samples, plus gather these tracks!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66607,'en','Snow & Cherry Blossoms','Hunt all target monsters','Hey, I came across a couple of truly terrifying monsters in the Coral Highlands. Thought you might be interested! (Bonus HR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66608,'en','A Nose for an Eye','Hunt all target monsters','In my day, we didn''t need these Scoutflies to track down monsters, but this is the New World... I''ve located some interesting monsters for you. Go get them. (Bonus HR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66609,'en','No Tomorrow for Usurpers','Hunt Bazelgeuse','Our guys spotted that big, ugly flying nuisance in the Elder''s Recess! Get your gear, we need you out here ASAP! (Bonus HR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66610,'en','The Thronetaker','Slay all target monsters','I finally got permission from Botanical Research to go out in the field. My partners and I stumbled upon a Teostra, Lunastra AND Nergigante! My luck freakin'' sucks! I need a nap...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(50901,'en','Banquet in the Earthen Hall','Repel Kulve Taroth','The mother goddess has appeared again, but now that we have the Fifth here, we can finally complete the investigation that we started decades ago! We''re counting on you kids!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63004,'en','Down the Dark, Muddy Path','Slay a Barroth','I heard rumors of a powerful monster dwelling in this place. One clad in an armor of earth. You must be like myself, seeking a rival that will force you to surpass your limits. It''s time to fight!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63005,'en','USJ Beginners Challenge!','Slay a Kulu-Ya-Ku','Hello everyone, and welcome to USJ! We''re happy to introduce our latest quest attraction, perfectly suitable for beginners! Come on and enjoy yourselves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63006,'en','USJ Expert Challenge!','Slay a Rathian','Hello everyone, and welcome to USJ! We''re happy to introduce our latest quest attraction, perfect for those who can beat up a monster with one arm tied behind their back!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63007,'en','USJ Beginners Challenge!','Slay a Tzitzi-Ya-Ku','Hello everyone, and welcome to USJ! We''re happy to introduce our latest quest attraction, perfectly suitable for beginners! Come on and enjoy yourselves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63008,'en','USJ Expert Challenge!','Slay a Rathalos','Hello everyone, and welcome to USJ! We''re happy to introduce our latest quest attraction, perfect for those who can beat up a monster with one arm tied behind their back!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63009,'en','Down the Dark, Muddy Path','Slay a Barroth','I heard rumors of a powerful monster dwelling in this place. One clad in an armor of earth. You must be like myself, seeking a rival that will force you to surpass your limits. It''s time to fight!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63034,'en','The Awakened Satsui No Hado I','Slay Nergigante','Hah, you''ve come to fight a real boss of a dragon, eh? Don''t worry, I won''t say a word about this. You just go and stop that thing with all you''ve got!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63035,'en','The Awakened Satsui No Hado II','Slay Nergigante','Hah, you''ve come to fight a real boss of a dragon, eh? Don''t worry, I won''t say a word about this. You just go and stop that thing with all you''ve got!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63036,'en','The Awakened Satsui No Hado III','Slay Nergigante','Hah, you''ve come to fight a real boss of a dragon, eh? Don''t worry, I won''t say a word about this. You just go and stop that thing with all you''ve got!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63037,'en','Empress in Full Bloom I','Slay Pink Rathian','They say there''s a monster as pink as the cherry blossoms around these parts, is that true!? Let''s see who''s the strongest, you, me, or that monster! Winner gets a prize!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63038,'en','Empress in Full Bloom II','Slay Pink Rathian','They say there''s a monster as pink as the cherry blossoms around these parts, is that true!? Let''s see who''s the strongest, you, me, or that monster! Winner gets a prize!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63039,'en','Empress in Full Bloom III','Slay Pink Rathian','They say there''s a monster as pink as the cherry blossoms around these parts, is that true!? Let''s see who''s the strongest, you, me, or that monster! Winner gets a prize!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3101,'en','Arena Quest 01','Slay a Pukei-Pukei','In the monster corner: Pukei-Pukei, the Toxic Tussler, the Lickin'' Machine! He won''t listen when you say "no tongues"! Who''s got the guts to fight it with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3001,'en','Arena Quest 02','Slay a Kulu-Ya-Ku','In the monster corner: Kulu-Ya-Ku, the Pulverizer, the Peckanizer! If this bird is the word, then the word is SMASH! Who''s got the guts to fight it with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3002,'en','Arena Quest 03','Slay a Rathian','In the monster corner: Rathian, the Queen o'' Green, the Skyborne Slasher! Don''t get the lady angry; she''s poison! Who''s got the guts to fight her with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3031,'en','Arena Quest 04','Slay a Tzitzi-Ya-Ku','In the monster corner: Tzitzi-Ya-Ku, the Saurian Stunner, the Flashinator! This beastie''s hot to trot and fine to shine! Who''s got the guts to fight it with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3032,'en','Arena Quest 05','Slay a Barroth','In the monster corner: Barroth, the Hulking Headbutt, the Skullcracker! Lose to this guy, and your name is mud! Who''s got the guts to fight it with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3033,'en','Arena Quest 06','Slay a Dodogama','In the monster corner: Dodogama, the Behemoth of Boom, the Cruncher! What blows up, must bring you down! Who''s got the guts to fight it with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3034,'en','Arena Quest 07','Slay an Azure Rathalos','In the monster corner: Azure Rathalos, the Sapphire Sultan, the True Blue Terror! Bow down to the king of all wyverns! Who''s got the guts to fight it with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3051,'en','Arena Quest 08','Slay all target monsters','In the monster corner: A Radobaan-Uragaan tag team! The wheels are turning, and your number''s up! Who''s got the guts to fight ''em with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3052,'en','Arena Quest 09','Slay all target monsters','In the monster corner: A Diablos-Black Diablos tag team! Ever had your ears pierced? Now try the extreme version! Who''s got the guts to fight ''em with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63033,'en','Gajalaka Outbreak!','Defeat 10 Gajalaka','Geez, I just wanted to study the Gajalaka language, so I brought a group of them with me, but they all ran away! Can you help me round them up before they get into trouble?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63104,'en','Gale & Fangs Slay Event 1','Slay all target monsters','To the hunters who have conquered the New World using everything at your disposal, we salute you with a quest that will show us why they call you the true Sapphire Star!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63105,'en','Gale & Fangs Slay Event 2','Slay all target monsters','To the hunters who have conquered the New World using everything at your disposal, we salute you with a quest that will show us why they call you the true Sapphire Star!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63106,'en','Gale & Fangs Slay Event 3','Slay all target monsters','To the hunters who have conquered the New World using everything at your disposal, we salute you with a quest that will show us why they call you the true Sapphire Star!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63101,'en','Nergigante Slay Event 1','Slay Nergigante','To the hunters who have conquered the New World using everything at your disposal, we salute you with a quest that will show us why they call you the true Sapphire Star!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63102,'en','Nergigante Slay Event 2','Slay Nergigante','To the hunters who have conquered the New World using everything at your disposal, we salute you with a quest that will show us why they call you the true Sapphire Star!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63103,'en','Nergigante Slay Event 3','Slay Nergigante','To the hunters who have conquered the New World using everything at your disposal, we salute you with a quest that will show us why they call you the true Sapphire Star!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63107,'en','Nergigante Slay Event 4','Slay Nergigante','To the hunters who have conquered the New World using everything at your disposal, we salute you with a quest that will show us why they call you the true Sapphire Star!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63108,'en','Deviljho Slay Event','Slay a Deviljho','We can''t lavish any more praise on a hunter such as yourself, who has survived the dangers of the New World. But we do have a quest that will challenge even you, our Sapphire Star!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63109,'en','The Best of the Best','Slay all target monsters','We can''t lavish any more praise on a hunter such as yourself, who has survived the dangers of the New World. But we do have a quest that will challenge even you, our Sapphire Star!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63110,'en','What Lurks In The Forest','Slay all target monsters','We can''t lavish any more praise on a hunter such as yourself, who has survived the dangers of the New World. But we do have a quest that will challenge even you, our Sapphire Star!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63130,'en','When Law Meets War','Slay a Bazelgeuse','Only a hunter like you, who has survived the dangers of the New World, can stand tall until the end and show everyone who has a heart that will not succumb to adversity!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63131,'en','The Hunter and The Blue Empress','Slay a Lunastra','Only a hunter like you, who has survived the dangers of the New World, can stand tall until the end and show everyone who has the fieriest of hearts!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61101,'en','Up at the Crack of Dawn','Slay 12 Kestodon','"Our friendly Kestodon have blown a gasket, so we let them cool off in your Arena. Research Commission friends, please see if they''ve settled down." (Translation by the Lynian Researcher)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63003,'en','Vespoid Infestation!','Slay 30 Vespoid','Oh deeeear! I placed some monster repellent around here, but it started attracting giant Vespoids too! Someone, anyone, I need an exterminator!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63001,'en','Challenge Quest 1: Beginner','Slay all target monsters','In the monster corner: Two fringed contenders guaranteed to ruffle your feathers! Below the belt shots are allowed! You''re the only one with a belt, so watch out!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63002,'en','Challenge Quest 2: Beginner','Slay all target monsters','In the monster corner: A Paolumu and Tobi-Kadachi tag team! One zips and zaps while the other drifts and flips! Wouldn''t you know it, they make good enemies, but better friends!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63031,'en','Challenge Quest 1: Intermediate','Slay all target monsters','In the monster corner: A Rathalos and Tzitzi-Ya-Ku tag team! Fighting a war on two fronts is never fun, but maybe one of the monsters can *ahem* shed some light on a viable strategy!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63032,'en','Challenge Quest 2: Intermediate','Slay 2 Odogaron','In the monster corner: A double dose of Odogaron! Any hunter brave enough to step into their penitentiary should prepare for the most brutal of sentences!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63051,'en','Challenge Quest 1: Expert','Slay all target monsters','In the monster corner: A Bazelgeuse-Uragaan tag team! You''re walking into a literal minefield with these two around! Watch your step and you won''t get blown up!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63052,'en','Challenge Quest 2: Expert','Slay Nergigante','In the monster corner: Nergigante, the Divebombing Demon, the Prickly Punisher, the Barbed Brawler. It''s half past time for the Eater of Elder''s next meal, and you''re on the menu!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1101,'en','Baptism by Ice','Hunt a Beotodus','Ready to get exploring, Pard? I can hardly imagine what secrets are hidden beneath the snow! I''ll find a place for the airship to land, you secure the area!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1102,'en','Banbaro Blockade','Hunt a Banbaro','I''ve arranged a shipment of supplies from Astera, which should arrive at any moment. We''ll need you to secure the Hoarfrost Reach to ensure it arrives safely. Don''t forget to bundle up.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1201,'en','Ready to Strike','Hunt a Viper Tobi-Kadachi','The scoutflies are useless with that Viper Tobi-Kadachi around. Get in there and do what you do best so we can keep pushing forward.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1202,'en','No Time for Naps','Hunt a Nightshade Paolumu','Target: Nightshade Paolumu. Reports indicate that first contact resulted in extreme drowsiness. That''s where the report ends... Let''s get to it, uh, Partner! Excited to see what you can do!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1203,'en','Play Both Ends','Hunt a Coral Pukei-Pukei','Target: Coral Pukei-Pukei. Reports indicate that first contact was greeted with blasts of...water? That''s where the report ends... Let''s get to it, uh, Partner! Excited to see what you can do!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1301,'en','Blizzard Blitz','Hunt a Barioth','Reports have been coming in about a Barioth roaming around the Reach. Those two are still examining the wreckage, but we''ll need them to retreat for now. Get out there and bring them back safely!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1302,'en','Ever-present Shadow','Hunt a Nargacuga','Velkhana''s arrival in the New World has thrown the ecosystem out of whack. I guess it was inevitable that a monster like a Nargacuga would show up. Get out there and take care of it.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1303,'en','The Scorching Blade','Hunt a Glavenus','Velkhana''s arrival in the New World has thrown the ecosystem out of whack. I guess it was inevitable that a monster like a Glavenus would show up. Get out there and take care of it.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1304,'en','Absolute Power','Hunt a Tigrex','New monsters are popping up everywhere due to Velkhana''s influence, even in the Rotten Vale. Head out and investigate this Tigrex. Be cautious of its piercing roar.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1305,'en','A Smashing Cross Counter','Hunt a Brachydios','New monsters are popping up everywhere due to Velkhana''s influence, even in the Elder''s Recess. Head out and investigate this Brachydios. Be cautious of its explosive slime attacks.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1306,'en','A Tale of Ice and Fire','Repel Velkhana','Thanks to everyone''s diligent efforts, we know that Velkhana is in the Elder''s Recess. We don''t know why it''s there, but we need our best hunters on the job. That means you!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1401,'en','When the Mist Taketh You','Hunt a Shrieking Legiana','Leave finding the Tracker to me. In the meantime, secure the area by taking care of that Legiana! Be careful though, there''s something off about this one...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1402,'en','The Disintegrating Blade','Hunt an Acidic Glavenus','As soon as Velkhana left, monsters everywhere started getting riled up. We''re short on manpower, and we need a hunter to secure the defense convoy''s route to Seliana. Start by taking out the Glavenus subspecies!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1403,'en','Bad Friends, Great Enemies','Hunt an Ebony Odogaron','As soon as Velkhana left, monsters everywhere started getting riled up. We''re short on manpower, and we need a hunter to secure the defense convoy''s route to Seliana. Start by taking out the Odogaron subspecies!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1404,'en','The Defense of Seliana','Complete the assignment','Velkhana is closing in on Seliana! Man the Dragonrazer and drive that thing back! All of Seliana is counting on you, Sapphire Star!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1405,'en','The Thunderous Troublemaker!','Hunt a Fulgur Anjanath','The convoy from Astera is approaching the Hoarfrost Reach, but we need to secure its route. Our favorite troublemaker is back, and someone needs to teach it a lesson!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1501,'en','The Iceborne Wyvern','Slay a Velkhana','We may have protected Seliana this time, but we still have no idea if and when Velkhana will return. It''s time to take the fight to the beast before it recovers! Gear up and head out! And BE CAREFUL!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1502,'en','The Second Coming','Hunt a Seething Bazelgeuse','Hah, look who''s back to wreak havoc. This guy thinks he owns the place, but he''s about to get a real rude awakening, right, Fiver? Get in there and send ''em packin''!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1503,'en','Under the Veil of Death','Slay a Blackveil Vaal Hazak','Something strange is going on... A Vaal Hazak has shown up in the Ancient Forest. Reports state that something is...off about it. What''s it doing outside the vale? At any rate, be careful!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1504,'en','A Light From The Abyss','Slay a Namielle','The Commission has discovered a never-before-seen elder dragon in the Coral Highlands. No solid info to go on, other than reports of an ominous light radiating from the highest plateau...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1601,'en','To The Guided, A Paean','Complete the assignment','Board the ship when you''re ready. It''s time we wrap up all loose ends. Who knows what we''ll find when we land, but I know you''ll be ready. You always are.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1602,'en','Paean of Guidance','Complete the assignment','The time has finally come to face Shara Ishvalda. I wish I could be there to have a good look at it... But this is a job only you''re capable of. Good luck.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1603,'en','Sleep Now in the Fire','Hunt all target monsters','This assignment is only for the few heroic hunters who can handle the rigors of being a true master hunter. Show everyone what you''re capable of! (Completing this quest unlocks the MR cap limit)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1604,'en','Big Burly Bash','Hunt all target monsters','This assignment is only for the few heroic hunters who can handle the rigors of being a true master hunter. Show everyone what you''re capable of! (Completing this quest unlocks the MR cap limit)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1606,'en','Return of the Crazy One','Hunt a Yian Garuga','What!? A Yian Garuga!? According to my notes, these monsters will pick a fight with just about anything! It also says be careful around its supersonic roars. This is gonna be exciting, Pard!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1121,'en','Deep Snow Diver','Hunt a Beotodus','Beotodus is a fascinating piscine wyvern that has the ability to "swim" through the snow. How it is actually able to do this is a mystery. I must have more data on this creature!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1122,'en','Taking Charge','Hunt a Banbaro','—and by the by, you''ve locked horns with the gigantic Banbaro, yes? Thick fur to protect against the cold, and those massive horns! Simply astounding, yes? Oh, and the way it char—');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1123,'en','Ice Catch!','Capture a Beotodus','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You go out and get me them materials and I''ll see if I can sneak in an upgrade! (Upgrades the Ghillie Mantle upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1124,'en','Call of the Wild','Slay 10 Wulg','Those Wulg are an interesting bunch! They don''t go in for the kill right away. Nope! They wait for a chance, and then call in their buddies to help. Maaan, I love researching!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1125,'en','Greetings from the Tundra','Deliver 20 Young Butterburs','Bossman says he wants to examine some Young Butterburs, so do me a solid and grab some for me, will you? Says he''ll upgrade the Harvest Box for you in return! (First completion upgrades the Harvest Box)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1131,'en','Special Arena: MR Pukei-Pukei','Hunt a Pukei-Pukei','A new challenger: Pukei-Pukei, the Toxic Tussler, the Lickin'' Machine! He won''t listen when you say "no tongues"! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1132,'en','Special Arena: MR Barroth','Hunt a Barroth','A new challenger: Barroth, the Hulking Headbutt, the Skullcracker! Lose to this guy, and your name is mud! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1133,'en','Special Arena: MR Tobi-Kadachi','Hunt a Tobi-Kadachi','A new challenger: Tobi-Kadachi, the Leaping Lizard, the Bitemaster! He''ll clean your clock with thunder shocks! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1134,'en','Special Arena: MR Banbaro','Hunt a Banbaro','A new challenger: Banbaro, the Ruler of the Reach, the Champ of Tramp! If you can''t dig your own grave, he''ll dig it for you! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1151,'en','The Great Jagras Returns!','Hunt a Great Jagras','I need to consult with the First Wyverians about this new decoration I want to create, but there''s some bloated lizard standing in the way. Be a dear and please take care of it, will you?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1152,'en','New World Problems','Hunt a Pukei-Pukei','It''s nearly impossible to obtain a sample from the Ancient Forest without it being contaminated by that blasted monster''s poisonous slobber! Please, Hunter. Deal with it, won''t you?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1153,'en','Beating Around the Bush','Hunt a Tobi-Kadachi','One of my researchers is out in the Ancient Forest hiding in a bush because he''s "afraid" of a Tobi-Kadachi. I know he''s just dawdling about. Please dispatch the monster so he can get back to work!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1154,'en','Literary Thief','Hunt a Kulu-Ya-Ku','One of those blasted Kulu-Ya-Ku has stolen a very dear book that I leant to a field researcher. Take care of that despicable creature at once. Oh, and I suppose check on the researcher if you have time...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1155,'en','Trapping The Tree Trasher','Capture a Banbaro','Tail shakes alive, this meownster is gettin'' on my last nerve! Can you please go out there and smack that overgrown pot roast upside the head so we can get these ingredients? (Canteen ingredients added upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1161,'en','Wildspire Treasure Hunt','Hunt a Kulu-Ya-Ku','We''ve got reports coming in from all locations confirming the existence of some unusually tough monsters. Head to their locations and begin your investigations ASAP.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1162,'en','Dragged Through the Mud','Hunt a Barroth','Accounting has been going on and on about how much zenny we spend on laundry. Well perhaps if there wasn''t a Barroth out in the wastes flinging mud everywhere we could stay within our budget!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1163,'en','Jyura In My Way','Hunt a Jyuratodus','I need to consult with the First Wyverians about this new decoration I want to create, but there''s a Joora...Jeeura—a big ugly fish in the way! Be a dear and please take care of it, will you?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1164,'en','Taster''s Tour','Hunt a Pukei-Pukei','We''ve got reports coming in from all locations confirming the existence of some unusually tough monsters. Head to their locations and begin your investigations ASAP.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1171,'en','All the Wrong Signals','Hunt a Tzitzi-Ya-Ku','One of my researchers was out testing a prototype feature of the Surveyor Set when a Tzitzi-Ya-Ku mistook the flash as territorial threat. The researcher panicked and dropped the device. If we are to ever recover it, we''ll need you to dispatch the creature first.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1181,'en','Grinding my Girros','Hunt a Great Girros','It''s already quite difficult to get ANY research done in the Rotten Vale as it is. Merely existing in the vale without proper protection is enough to end you. And now a Great Girros has shown up with its little minions to complicate our work. Hunter, if you would, please.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1191,'en','Can''t Bring Yourself To It','Hunt a Dodogama','We''re facing a rather unique issue at the moment. Research in the recess has come to a halt due to a rather rambunctious Dodogama. However, most of our hunters are refusing to hunt it because they think Dodogama are..."cute."');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1192,'en','This Here''s Big Horn Country!','Hunt a Banbaro','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. It''s vital that you go out and get me them materials so I can get to work! (Upgrades the Vitality Mantle upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1221,'en','Analysis Creates Paralysis','Hunt a Viper Tobi-Kadachi','Can''t...move... Bitten...by...a Viper...Tobi-Kadachi... Poison...seeping...into...my bloodstream... In...lots...of trouble... Help...me...please...!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1222,'en','Poison and Paralysis Pinch','Capture a Viper Tobi-Kadachi','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You go out and get me them materials and I''ll see if I can boost your tools with an upgrade! (Upgrades the Cleanser Booster upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1223,'en','Boaboa Constrictor','Defeat 14 Boaboa','Duuuude! I got these sick drafts cooked up! Just, uh, they need a few more tweaks. Yo, help me out with this quest, and stuff, and you can get a special ticket. Pretty sweet, right?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1224,'en','By Our Powers Combined','Hunt a Beotodus','Our target of this joint operation is the fearsome Beotodus! First, drive a Popo out in the open to lure the monster out. Then when that frosty fishy takes the bait, we''ll ambush it!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1225,'en','You Scratch Our Backs...','Hunt a Beotodus','Thanks to your efforts, we''ve made fellowship with the local Lynians! I''d like to pay them a visit, but a meddling Beotodus is in the way. Please, for science, assist me!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1231,'en','Special Arena: MR Anjanath','Hunt an Anjanath','A new challenger: Anjanath, the Jaws of Death, the Stompasaurus! He''s just stopped by for a quick bite! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1232,'en','Special Arena: MR Radobaan','Hunt a Radobaan','A new challenger: Radobaan, the Roto-Ravager, the Grinder! Better dodge fast, or you''ll be boned! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1233,'en','Special Arena: MR Coral Pukei-Pukei','Hunt a Coral Pukei-Pukei','A new challenger: Coral Pukei-Pukei, the Savage Sprayer, the Blast Master! Watch out or he''ll take you to the cleaners! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1234,'en','Special Arena: MR Viper Tobi-Kadachi','Hunt a Viper Tobi-Kadachi','A new challenger: Viper Tobi-Kadachi, The Boss of Blight, the Number One Stunner! He bites you, you bite the dust! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1235,'en','Special Arena: MR Rathian','Hunt a Rathian','A new challenger: Rathian, the Queen o'' Green, the Skyborne Slasher! Don''t get the lady angry; she''s poison! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1236,'en','Special Arena: MR Pink Rathian','Hunt a Pink Rathian','A new challenger: Pink Rathian, the Burning Blossom, the Beauty Who Bites! Best not stop to smell the roses! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1237,'en','Special Arena: MR Paolumu','Hunt a Paolumu','A new challenger: Paolumu, the Punishing Puffball, the Fearigible! It may not be fair, but he''s walking on air! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1238,'en','Special Arena: MR Nightshade Paolumu','Hunt a Nightshade Paolumu','A new challenger: Nightshade Paolumu, the Sultan of Slumber, the Flightmare! Get caught in the sleeper hold, and it''s lights out! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1251,'en','Anjanath Antics','Hunt an Anjanath','I swear, if I have to handle one more report covered in snot, I''m going to have a fit! Is there not anything that disgusting beast won''t blow its mucus all over!?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1252,'en','Fool''s Mate','Hunt a Rathian','Dear Gog... One of my researchers is absolutely obsessed with a particular Rathian he has been observing. So much so that he rarely returns to base anymore to report. I ask that you do something about it before things get...weird.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1253,'en','Nighty Night Nightshade','Capture a Nightshade Paolumu','Tail shakes alive, this meownster is gettin'' on my last nerve! Can you please go out there and smack that ugly thing upside its ugly head so we can get these ingredients? (Canteen ingredients added upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1261,'en','A Queen At Heart','Hunt a Rathian','I want to speak with a First Wyverian about a decoration I want to meld, but the Commander won''t let me go out with all these "big scary" monsters around. Can you "hang a girl up?" as you kids say.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1262,'en','A Face Nightmares Are Made Of','Hunt a Nightshade Paolumu','There I was, minding meow-n business, when suddenly the ugliest face I''d ever seen jumped out at me. I must have fainted, but when I came to, it was gone. I know it''s still out there... Out there with its hideous face! Please, Hunter! I still have nightmares about it!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1263,'en','Stick Your Nose Somewhere Else','Hunt an Anjanath','We''ve got reports coming in from all locations confirming the existence of some unusually tough monsters. Head to their locations and begin your investigations ASAP.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1264,'en','Feisty Girl Talk','Hunt all target monsters','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You go out and get me them materials and I''ll make sure your tools get a healthy upgrade! (Upgrades the Health Booster upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1271,'en','The Plight of Paolumu','Hunt a Paolumu','As operations in the Hinterlands expand further, our researchers require gear that is not only well-insulated but comfortable for long hours of field work. I''m interested in having a prototype developed, however I''ll need some materials before we can start.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1272,'en','Pink Power Grab','Hunt a Pink Rathian','The exodus of Legiana has created a power vacuum in the Coral Highlands. A rather fearsome Pink Rathian seems inclined to fill that void. However, her reign is having a detrimental effect on the food chain. I ask that you go out and usurp the throne, Hunter!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1273,'en','Protip: Stay Hydrated','Hunt a Coral Pukei-Pukei','Coral Pukei-Pukei possess specialized organs to store the water they consume. I''d like to have a closer look at it for my notes, so I''ll have to call in a favor just this once, Hunter.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1274,'en','Put That Red Cup Away','Hunt a Coral Pukei-Pukei','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. This mantle may be waterproof but it sure as heck ain''t upgrade-proof! (Upgrades the Waterproof Mantle upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1281,'en','No Laughing Matter','Hunt a Radobaan','Oh, dear...hahaha! One of my researchers *snicker* was attacked by a Radobaan and—as she was running away—all of her research notes got stuck to the tar on its body. So, as we speak, there''s a Radobaan rolling around the vale with her life''s work glued to it... BWAHAHAHA!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1282,'en','Bugger Off Bugs!','Slay all target monsters','I want to speak with a First Wyverian about a decoration I want to meld, but the Commander won''t let me go out with all these "big scary" monsters around. Can you "hang a girl up?" as you kids say.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1291,'en','Looking For That Glimmer','Deliver 20 Gaia Ambers','Bossman says he''s got some theories about Gaia Amber that he''d like to test. In return for your help, he''ll upgrade the Harvest Box. (Upgrades the Harvest Box upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1321,'en','Remember That One Time?','Hunt a Barioth','So yeah, the Barioth...a violent snowstorm personified. It reminds me of this one time I had to go on a hunt for... You know what? Never mind. I''ll leave this to you.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1322,'en','The Purr-fect Room: Stone','Capture a Tigrex','P.U.R.R. is in fur effect...with just one minor hiccup: a Tigrex! Nab that angry tabby while we sneak past to grab the goods! (Room decoration added upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1323,'en','Proud White Knight','Hunt a Barioth','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You get me them materials and this upgrade will have you bobbin'' and weavin'' like there''s no tomorrow! (Upgrades the Evasion Mantle upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1331,'en','Special Arena: MR Legiana','Hunt a Legiana','A new challenger: Legiana, the Slipstream Striker, the Wingleader! Remember, you can''t spell flight without fight! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1332,'en','Special Arena: MR Odogaron','Hunt an Odogaron','A new challenger: Odogaron, the Muscle Mutt, the Rex Who Wrecks! He''ll bite your leg to fetch the stick inside! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1333,'en','Special Arena: MR Uragaan','Hunt an Uragaan','A new challenger: Uragaan, the Rolling Rocket, the Chinstigator! Once he starts spinning, uragoner! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1334,'en','Special Arena: MR Rathalos','Hunt a Rathalos','A new challenger: Rathalos, the Red-Hot Raider, the Firestarter! Forgive the fireballs; he likes his meals cooked! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1335,'en','Special Arena: MR Diablos','Hunt a Diablos','A new challenger: Diablos, the Sandy Stampede, Biggus Diggus! Don''t hang around if he''s underground! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1336,'en','Special Arena: MR Barioth','Hunt a Barioth','A new challenger: Barioth, the Tusked Terror, The Baron of Blizzards! First everything''s white, then it turns black! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1337,'en','Special Arena: MR Nargacuga','Hunt a Nargacuga','A new challenger: Nargacuga, the Shadowy Slayer, the Nimble Ninja! If you can''t see him, it''s already too late! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1338,'en','Special Arena: MR Glavenus','Hunt a Glavenus','A new challenger: Glavenus, the Cauterizer, the Slasha-saurus! With this monster, every match is a split decision! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1339,'en','Special Arena: MR Brachydios','Hunt a Brachydios','A new challenger: Brachydios, the Guru of Goo, The Purple Pounder! Says he''s looking for some chump called "Doodle." Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1340,'en','Special Arena: MR Tigrex','Hunt a Tigrex','A new challenger: Tigrex, the Rushing Rampager, the Emperoar! This monster puts the arm in harm! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1351,'en','Swoop to a New Low','Hunt a Rathalos','Blasted Rathalos! Every time the field team tags an Aptonoth to track its behavior, this confounded creature swoops in and carries it off! It''s almost as if it''s doing it on purpose!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1352,'en','Nargacoulda, Shoulda, Woulda','Hunt a Nargacuga','I should know better than to go out into the Ancient Forest without a hunter escort, but I didn''t think a freakin'' Nargacuga would be there! Why didn''t anybody tell me!? Help me, PLEASE!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1353,'en','The Secret to a Good Slice','Hunt a Glavenus','Some of the newly discovered monsters in the New World have been sighted in other locales. The shift in surroundings will most likely have a significant effect on their behavior, head to their location and investigate immediately.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1354,'en','Red and Black Aces','Hunt all target monsters','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You go out and get me them materials I need and I''ll make sure your mantle soars to new heights! (Upgrades the Glider Mantle upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1361,'en','A Line in the Sand','Hunt a Diablos','Our researchers are finding it nearly impossible to study the cacti out in the wastes. Even attempting to get close to a cactus patch triggers a Diablos attack from below...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1362,'en','A Flash of the Blade','Hunt a Glavenus','—and by the by, you''ve crossed blades with the fearsome Glavenus, yes? The way it wields its gleaming, sword tail! Simply astounding, yes? Oh, and how it sharpens it in its—');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1363,'en','Simmer and Slice!','Hunt all target monsters','Tail shakes alive, these meownsters are gettin'' on my last nerve! Can you please go out there and smack those two upside the head so we can get these ingredients? (Canteen ingredients added upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1371,'en','Legiana Left Behind','Hunt a Legiana','Due to the Legiana migrating to the Hinterlands, there has been a shortage of specimen to study in the Coral Highlands. However, a straggler has been spotted recently. We can''t let this opportunity go to waste!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1372,'en','The Black Wind','Hunt a Nargacuga','Some of the newly discovered monsters in the New World have been sighted in other locales. The shift in surroundings will most likely have a significant effect on their behavior, head to their location and investigate immediately.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1373,'en','A Nasty Flesh Wound','Hunt an Odogaron','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You go out and snatch the materials I need and I''ll sneak an upgrade into your tools! (Upgrades the Bandit Mantle upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1381,'en','Don''t be a Jerk with the Jerky','Hunt an Odogaron','One of my less forward-thinking researchers has quite an affinity for snacks, especially Astera jerky. I''ve told him time and again to only eat them when necessary but now he''s really in trouble. An Odogaron has attacked him and without any jerky, I''m afraid he may be done for...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1382,'en','A Roar that Shook the Vale','Hunt a Tigrex','It''s well-known that the Tigrex is a primitive flying wyvern, which means investigating its appearance in the New World could teach us much about other flying wyverns here!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1383,'en','Runnin'', Rollin'', and Weepin''','Hunt all target monsters','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. It''ll hardly be a challenge to upgrade your gear if you go out and get me the materials I need! (Upgrades the Challenger Mantle upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1391,'en','Blast Warning In Effect!','Hunt a Brachydios','—and by the by, you''ve exchanged blows with the Brachydios, yes? Most clamor over its peculiar slime, but not I! No, I''m all about those fists! Yes, the way it strikes the ground and—');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1392,'en','Everyone''s a Critic','Hunt a Lavasioth','Whilst one of our artists was out trying to paint a landscape of the recess, a Lavasioth appeared out of nowhere and attacked. Though he survived the ordeal, his commissioned piece did not. Please make your way out there and secure the area so that he may continue his work.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1393,'en','Begone Uragaan','Hunt an Uragaan','The infirmary is overflowing with researchers suffering from extreme vertigo. The cause? One of those blasted Uragaan rolling about. Go out there and put the brakes on its spinning!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1394,'en','Secret of the Ooze','Capture a Brachydios','I''d like to experiment with that peculiar slime the Brachydios secretes—oh, it''ll be 100% safe, don''t you worry! Heh... And if you help, I''m sure it''ll help our Ancient Tree some, too! (Unlocks a Botanical Research slot on first time completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1395,'en','Festival of Explosions!','Hunt all target monsters','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You get me the materials I need and I''ll make sure your gear''s upgrade''ll be straight fire! (Upgrades the Fireproof Mantle upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1421,'en','Noblefrost Hunter','Hunt a Shrieking Legiana','How that Legiana got a cloak of ice like that is a mystery, but it''s nothing science can''t solve! We''ll need all the data you can get on that thing!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1422,'en','Tundra Troublemaker','Hunt a Fulgur Anjanath','—and by the by, you''ve come snout to snout with the Fulgur Anjanath, yes? How a brute wyvern could somehow make its way to the Hinterlands! Astounding, yes? How can it even swi—');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1423,'en','Duet of Rime','Hunt all target monsters','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You go out and get me the materials I need and I''ll hook you up with a cool upgrade! (Upgrades the Iceproof Mantle upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1424,'en','Treasure in the Steam','Deliver 2 Hot Spring Stones','Duuuude! I got these sick drafts cooked up! Just, uh, they need a few more tweaks. Yo, help me out with this quest, and stuff, and you can get a special ticket. Pretty sweet, right?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1431,'en','Special Arena: MR Azure Rathalos','Hunt an Azure Rathalos','A new challenger: Azure Rathalos, the Sapphire Sultan, the True Blue Terror! Bow down to the king of all wyverns! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1432,'en','Special Arena: MR Black Diablos','Hunt a Black Diablos','A new challenger: Black Diablos, the Dark Destroyer, the Horn Express! Run, don''t walk, from this furious fiend! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1433,'en','Special Arena: MR Acidic Glavenus','Hunt an Acidic Glavenus','A new challenger: Acidic Glavenus, the Colonel of Corrosion, The Dino Dueler! There''s no stoppin'' once he gets to choppin''! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1434,'en','Special Arena: MR Ebony Odogaron','Hunt an Ebony Odogaron','A new challenger: Ebony Odogaron, the Overlord of Onyx, the Hell-hound that Pounds! He''ll teach you to sit, roll over, and play dead! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1435,'en','Special Arena: MR Fulgur Anjanath','Hunt a Fulgur Anjanath','A new challenger: Fulgur Anjanath, the Shock-o-saurus, T-Wrecks! He''s electric! Boogie Woogie, Woogie! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1451,'en','These Azure Eyes See All','Hunt an Azure Rathalos','We''ve got reports coming in from all locations confirming the existence of some unusually tough monsters. Head to their locations and begin your investigations ASAP.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1452,'en','Misfortune in the Forest','Hunt an Ebony Odogaron','Some of the newly discovered monsters in the New World have been sighted in other locales. The shift in surroundings will most likely have a significant effect on their behavior, head to their location and investigate immediately.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1461,'en','In the Heat of the Moment','Hunt a Black Diablos','It seems that one of our researchers was set on by a Black Diablos and during the encounter he spilt attractant all over himself. Now the lovesick beast is chasing him all over the wastes...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1462,'en','Piercing Black','Hunt a Black Diablos','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You get me the materials I need and no monster will be knocking you around! (Upgrades the Rocksteady Mantle upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1471,'en','A Shadowy Offender','Hunt an Ebony Odogaron','"I''m on the trail of an Ebony Odogaron. It''s a ferocious monster that seems to have a thirst for battle. I must take care not—" (the rest of the note is torn...)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1481,'en','This Corroded Blade','Hunt an Acidic Glavenus','—and by the by, you''ve dueled with the Acidic Glavenus, yes? How it sharpens that dull, acidic tail into a beautiful blade! Simply astounding, yes! Oh, and the way it winds up for an—');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1482,'en','The Purr-fect Room: Light Iron','Capture an Acidic Glavenus','P.U.R.R. is in fur effect...with just one minor hiccup: an Acidic Glavenus! Bag us that Glavenus and we''ll sneak past and snatch the goods! (Decor materials for your room added upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1483,'en','The Purr-fect Room: Dark Iron','Hunt all target monsters','P.U.R.R. is in fur effect...with just one minor hiccup, well, actually two: a double dose of depraved devil doggies! Put ''em on a leash so we can go in and get the goods! (Decor materials for your room added upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1491,'en','Blue Rathalos Blues','Hunt an Azure Rathalos','Azure Rathalos are known to mark their territory with gashes by using their massive claws. As fascinating as this is to our ethology department, it''s quite a headache for our geologists.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1492,'en','Trap the Thunder Jaw','Capture a Fulgur Anjanath','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You get me the materials I need and I''ll upgrade your gear lightning-quick! (Upgrades the Thunderproof Mantle upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1521,'en','Clashing Swords Upon The Rime','Slay a Velkhana','Official records about Velkhana are non-existent, and much has yet to be confirmed about its ecology. But this is the perfect opportunity for us—er, YOU, to make history!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1551,'en','The Harbinger of Clear Skies','Slay a Kushala Daora','Sure, Kushala Daora wrecks things with its storms, but I think it gets a bad rap. I mean, after those storms, it''s super sunny and everything! Help me change people''s minds!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1552,'en','Here Comes the Deathmaker','Slay a Blackveil Vaal Hazak','...... So, the stories are true. A Vaal Hazak, in the Ancient Forest. Time for you to get to work, Hunter. Run along, now.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1561,'en','Royal Audience on the Sand','Slay a Teostra','A member of the Fourth encountered a Teostra in the Waste, one more terrible than usual. The emperor sits on its throne, waiting. Shall we pay him a visit?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1562,'en','The Tyrant''s Banquet','Hunt a Savage Deviljho','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You go out and get me the materials I need and the status of your gear is sure to go up! (Upgrades the Apothecary Mantle upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1571,'en','Lightning Crashes','Slay a Kirin','An unusual amount of lightning and radiance has occurred in the Highlands recently. This must be a sign that a Kirin is active in the area. You MUST look into this, Hunter!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1572,'en','Memories of the Sea God','Slay a Namielle','Namielle is a truly terrifying beast, capable of summoning torrents as well as lightning! We must gather as much data as possible. I ask that you head out immediately, and of course, be careful!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1581,'en','It''s the Afterlife for Me','Slay a Blackveil Vaal Hazak','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. Your gear might be immune to abnormal status effects but it ain''t immune to my upgrades! (Upgrades the Immunity Mantle upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1591,'en','Wings of the Wind','Slay a Kushala Daora','Black tornadoes have been spotted in the Elder''s Recess. Analytics believes this is the work of a Kushala Daora, and a very nasty one at that. I''ll leave this one to you, bud.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1592,'en','Mark of the Sun','Slay a Teostra','The Huntsman and I tried to take on a Teostra, but it was too much for us. We need you to head out to the Elder''s Recess and provide assistance. As in, you take care of it!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1593,'en','Seething with Anger','Hunt a Seething Bazelgeuse','So I heard this new Bazelgeuse is supposed to be red-hot. But do you think it can match MY red-hot passion for life? Uh, DOUBT IT! Let''s go out and cool down that fool!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1594,'en','The Purr-fect Room: Silver','Capture a Seething Bazelgeuse','P.U.R.R. is in fur effect...with just one minor hiccup: a Bazelgeuse! Maybe if you say its name three times, we can sneak in and get the goods! Go on, give it a try! (Decor materials for your room added upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1605,'en','To the Very Ends with You','Slay a Ruiner Nergigante','I know you''ve been waiting for this, and I bet Nergigante has, too. You guys are basically joined at the hip. But it''s time to end this. Go get ''em, Hunter! (Completing this quest unlocks the MR cap limit)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1631,'en','We Run This Town','Hunt all target monsters','You''ve overcome everything thrown at you so far, why not just one more challenge? Come out of this unscathed, and no one will forget why you''re the real Sapphire Star!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1632,'en','Special Arena: MR Zinogre','Hunt a Zinogre','A new challenger: Zinogre, the Bug Zapper, the Thunder Clapper! When this pup gets to howlin'', better throw the towel in! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1633,'en','Special Arena: MR Yian Garuga','Hunt a Yian Garuga','A new challenger: Yian Garuga, the Screamin'' Demon, the Beaked Berzerker! You''ve never seen crazy like this before! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1634,'en','Special Arena: MR Brute Tigrex','Hunt a Brute Tigrex','A new challenger: Brute Tigrex, the Aggro Assaulter, the Bellowing Blitzer! He''s talkin'' trash with the moves to back it up! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1635,'en','Special Arena: MR Gold Rathian','Hunt a Gold Rathian','A new challenger: Gold Rathian, The Queen of Sheen, the Lethal Lunar Lady! She may be golden but she''ll leave you black and blue. Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1636,'en','Special Arena: MR Silver Rathalos','Hunt a Silver Rathalos','A new challenger: Silver Rathalos, the Glistening Gladiator, the Fireball Flinger! He reigns over the ring with a rain of fire! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(51621,'en','Special Arena: MR Stygian Zinogre','Hunt a Stygian Zinogre','A new challenger: Stygian Zinogre, the Dean of Dracophage, the Mighty Mephisto! You better be hungry like the wolf if you wanna survive! Two fighters enter the Special Arena, but only one leaves!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1641,'en','Faraway Lorelei','Slay a Shara Ishvalda','Gotta admit, Shara Ishvalda is one elder dragon that is a sight to behold. Still can''t believe it led us all the way here. We still have much to learn, let''s pay it another visit!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1642,'en','Hymn of Moon and Sun','Hunt all target monsters','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You get me the materials I need and I guarantee this upgrade will have massive impact! (Upgrades the Impact Mantle upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1651,'en','The Storm Brings the Unexpected','Slay all target monsters','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You get me the materials I need and I guarantee you''ll just love this upgrade! (Upgrades the Affinity Booster upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1661,'en','One Hot Night in the Spire','Slay a Lunastra','Lunastra...I saw her just once and tried to express my feelings, but it was not meant to be. Oh, to be caressed by her flames... I need someone to tell her how I feel!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1671,'en','Divine Surge','Slay all target monsters','I''ve been going bonkers thinkin'' about how I can upgrade your specialized tools. You get me the materials I need and I''ll make sure your gear is truly next generation! (Upgrades the Temporal Mantle upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1691,'en','Into the Palace of Flame','Slay a Lunastra','A request to track down a Lunastra has come in! I wonder what it''s like to be treated like an empress. Take this quest, mon étoile, and show me...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(1692,'en','Master Hunter of the New World','Slay all target monsters','You''ve had your rough patches, but you''ve become a shining beacon for the Commission. So here''s to you, one last quest. May your name be etched in history!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(51602,'en','Sterling Pride','Slay a Kirin','You hear the rumors of ol'' Shattered Horn? Sounds like it''s shown up in the Hoarfrost Reach, but why it''s there and why its horn is broken is as clear as mud! Sounds like a mystery worth investigating, eh?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(51601,'en','Reveal Thyself, Destroyer','Complete the assignment','We''ve traced whatever broke the Kirin''s horn to the Guiding Lands. You can bet your bottom zenny that it''s one tough customer, so don''t let your guard down. And don''t be late!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(51603,'en','Across the Lost Path','Complete the assignment','We''ve discovered a new path in the Guiding Lands that even monsters tread carefully around. This may not be an issue from a long-term perspective, but it warrants an investigation.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(51604,'en','Point of No Return','Complete the assignment','We need you to do some recon on that red monster. Remember, don''t get in over your head. Get in, find out what you need, then get out.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(51606,'en','...And My Rage for All','Slay a Raging Brachydios','A Raging Brachydios has been spotted in the Guiding Lands. Not many hunters have faced one and come back in one piece. Think you can join their ranks?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(51607,'en','The Fury Remains','Hunt a Furious Rajang','A Furious Rajang has been spotted in the Hoarfrost Reach. Not many hunters have faced one and come back in one piece. Think you can join their ranks?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(51611,'en','Blazing Black Twilight','Slay an Alatreon','Not much is known of Alatreon, other than the destruction it''s capable of threatens all of humanity. But this is a chance for the Commission to write history, no?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67802,'en','Dawn''s Triumph','Slay an Alatreon','The burning Alatreon has once again been spotted. To make matters worse, news has spread of cataclysmic natural disasters occurring in the Old World. The timing of these events is curious to say the least. They merit further investigation but Alatreon comes first.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67803,'en','The Black Dragon','Slay Fatalis','It is time for us to confront Fatalis. We, along with every nation and organization known, shall rid this world of this fabled scourge. When you''re ready, we''ll set sail.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61801,'en','Pearl Snatchers','Deliver 6 Pearlspring Macaques','Ooooh! My best assistant came to lend me a hand! Think you can catch me some of those fluffy duffy Pearlspring Macaques? For what? Duh! To play with—er, I mean to research of course, you silly hunter! (Special material rewards upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(51605,'en','The Red Dragon','Slay Safi''jiiva','Safi''jiiva, the mature form of Xeno''jiiva... Reports confirm that it''s siphoning energy from its surroundings to heal its wounds. We need to eliminate this threat before it''s too late!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61805,'en','Duffel Duty','Deliver 8 Duffel Penguins','You ready to lend me a hand? Oh, goodie! I need you to capture some Duffel Penguins for me. You gotta be quick, though. They''ll give you the flipper then you give you the slip! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61811,'en','Flora Frostbite','Deliver 10 Iceblooms','The Reach is so cold your ears will fall off, or so I heard. Earmuffs would do the trick, or maybe some—!? I got it! Yes, INSPIRATION! To the message boards! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63142,'en','Farewell to the Frozen','Slay a Velkhana','To the hunters who have survived the dangers of the New World, I hope you can display your full potential one more time. Show them that the Sapphire Star can never be frozen!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66801,'en','Trophy Fishin''','Hunt all target monsters','Don''t think you can eat ''em and I know gramps would be reel upset if I plopped one down in front of him for supper. But sounds like mighty good fun tangoin'' with two tundra trouts! (Increased HR/MR points and special material rewards upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66802,'en','The Lord of the Underworld Beckons','Deliver 20 Underground Fruit','Those things—like felvine, I tell ya! I just can''t get enough! If you can go meow-t and get your paws on some more, I''d really a-purr-eciate it! I''ll even reward you with lots of bone materials fur your troubles! (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66803,'en','A Bunch of Sticks in the Mud','Hunt all target monsters','Some roaming Banbaro have adapted to the Wildspire and are using mounds of mud to attack hunters! Careful out there, everyone! (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66804,'en','Desert Desserts','Deliver 20 Hardfruit','Ah, Hunter! I''ve caught wind of a delicacy called a Hardfruit, which makes for a delightful snack. It''s a bit of a trek, but bring some back for me and I''ll reward you with lots of ore! (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61803,'en','Every Hunter''s Dream II','Capture a Coral Pukei-Pukei','A hunter came by with blueprints for Palico equipment they wanted me to craft. I still have the prints lying around, so if you want one of your own, get me the materials and I''ll start workin''. (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66805,'en','A New Troublemaker in Town','Hunt all target monsters','—and you know what would be fascinating? Hunting an Anjanath AND a Banbaro at the same time! I would certainly dole out more HR/MR points to any hunter who''d take up that challenge! Yes, can you imagine it, Hunter? Going at it with those two brutes—');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66807,'en','Hunter-Blunderer','Hunt all target monsters','We were supposed to go out to get some stuff for Analytics, but my partner goofed and went on a different quest! Can you take care of this while I fetch him? Geez...this bozo. (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66806,'en','Colorful Carnival','Hunt all target monsters','Yeah, time to get it done! I got an assignment from the scholars to pick up a couple of whatcha-ma-call-sacs. I''m gonna do it all in one go! (Increased HR/MR points upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61813,'en','50 Shades of White','Hunt a Barioth','To all hunters who yearn for action in the Arena, this quest is for you! Go head to head with our combatants, and earn special materials to craft weapons! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61802,'en','Every Hunter''s Dream III','Hunt all target monsters','A hunter came by with a blueprint of a weapon they wanted. I still have the prints lying around, so if you want one of your own, get me the materials and I''ll start workin''. (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66808,'en','A Sky & Sea of Fire','Hunt all target monsters','They''re everywhere! I can hear the treacherous wings of fire above me, and I can feel the smoldering glare coming from that lava! Help! (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66809,'en','A Curious Experiment','Hunt all target monsters','Hey, what do you think would happen if a Diablos charged at an inflated Paolumu? I''ve been thinking about this for way too long and now I can''t sleep. Do you think you can find out for me? (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66810,'en','Soaked and Shivering','Hunt all target monsters','I was SO looking forward to going out on a hunt in a place that''s not cold, but it IS cold. FREEZING COLD! And it''s wet too! That''s it! I am SO done. I''m going home... (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66811,'en','Fired-Up Bruisers','Hunt all target monsters','—to hunt a Glavenus AND an Uragaan simultaneously, yes! That''s the stuff dreams are made of! I''d most certainly dole out extra HR/MR points upon completion to the hunters who—');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66834,'en','When the Swift Meets the Roar','Hunt all target monsters','Expect things to get hot and tense in this quest! But don''t worry, you''ll get your fill of decorations if you come out of this in one piece! (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61812,'en','Beef is Never a Mi-steak','Hunt all target monsters','No matter how much I chow down, I''m never full. Guess I''m still a growing boy! I need my protein, or maybe—!? I got it! Yes, INSPIRATION! To the message boards! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66812,'en','The Desert Dash','Hunt all target monsters','Scouts have spotted a couple of highly dangerous monsters speeding across the Wildspire. Head to the locale and take care of both threats! And don''t be late! (Increased HR/MR points upon completion)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66814,'en','Servants of the Vale','Hunt all target monsters','Two monsters have staked claim to the Rotten Vale, Hunter. But no matter who wins, the Commission loses. We need someone like you to get in there and drive both of them out! (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66813,'en','In the Depths of the Forest','Hunt all target monsters','They say that Anjanaths are built for the forest. They roam it like kings, but now that an Azure Rathalos has showed up, we got a real fight on our hands! (Increased HR/MR points upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61806,'en','Scores of Ores','Hunt a Brachydios','Dang, mining is a workout! If I had a cooler pickaxe maybe this wou—...!? I got it! Yes, INSPIRATION! To the message boards! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61807,'en','A Chilling Entrance','Slay all target monsters','It''s cold today, better get a scarf to warm up. I wonder what''ll happen if I wrap my hea—...!? I got it! INSPIRATION! To the message boards! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66815,'en','We Three Kings','Slay all target monsters','Thunder. Wind. Fire. Nature''s wonders in their purest form. So, we fight purity with purity. Pick your weapon, hunter. And fight. (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66816,'en','The Winter Blues','Slay all target monsters','This cold reminds me of the Hinterlands, but it drips with an eerie, tranquil smell. This must be looked into, yes? Run along now... (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66817,'en','A Reason Behind The Hunger','Hunt a Savage Deviljho','Perhaps the reason why this type of Deviljho is constantly hunting is that it''s lost its ability to feel full? Perhaps I can empathize with its plight. I too, crave... My hunger for knowledge is insatiable! (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67801,'en','RE: Return of the Bioweapon','Slay a Blackveil Vaal Hazak','We''ve discovered a strange condition which is horrifyingly unaffected by <STYL MOJI_RED_DEFAULT>effluvial resistance! If it''s not effluvial buildup, then what is it? Help us, Hunter, and you''ll be generously compensated! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61814,'en','A Shocking Climax','Hunt all target monsters','I have located the ones who command the thunder. I left the task to a group of Fifth Fleet hunters, but they have yet to return. It''s up to you now. (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66818,'en','Moonlit Howl','Hunt a Zinogre','I saw a Zinogre in the Coral Highlands! This is it—the perfect opportunity for a study case on Fulgurbugs in the New World! I won''t rest until I—until YOU get me some specimens! (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66819,'en','I Am Tranquil, I Am Sound','Hunt a Yian Garuga','My purr-ank-loving furr-iend told me about this meownster that''s the definition of "calm"! I gotta see it for myself! Maybe I should take some earplugs...? Nah, I''ll be fine! (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66820,'en','A Roar that Splinters the Sky','Hunt a Brute Tigrex','As soon as we heard that roar in the distance, the hunter I was with sounded the retreat. Good thing, too—had we heard that roar up close, well, I''m sure I would have been its dinner! (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66821,'en','A Glance of Silver','Hunt a Silver Rathalos','At first I thought it was just some light glancing off the rocks in the Elder''s Recess, but it was HIM. I never thought I''d live to see this day! It makes me glad I came to the New World. (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66822,'en','The Moon is a Harsh Queen','Hunt a Gold Rathian','The golden empress has been spotted. We need the Fifth to prepare and head out. Take care, or the empress may turn the tables on you before you know it. (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61808,'en','Muscle Monkey Madness','Hunt 2 Rajang','Boy, I wish I could be as strong as you hunters! Maybe instead of getting buff, I could wear—!? I got it! Yes, INSPIRATION! To the message boards! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67804,'en','Mighty Muscle Monkey Madness','Hunt 2 Furious Rajang','Yeah, hunters are something else. "This won''t do... I''m not satisfied", they said with a fire in their eye. Their passion for muscles easily surpasses my inspiration! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66824,'en','Razzled, Frazzled, and Dazzled','Hunt a Rajang','The Admiral and some Fivers were talking some absolutely nonsense when they went off on a quest to hunt a Rajang. The Research Commission sure has a lot of hairballed hunters, huh? (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66825,'en','Scars Tell the Whole Story','Hunt a Scarred Yian Garuga','Us hunters have seen a lot of crazy stuff in our day, but nothing comes close to personifying crazy as that big purple chicken does! Don''t lose your cool now. (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66832,'en','Wolf Out of Hell','Hunt a Stygian Zinogre','My apologies. I spent years researching monsters, giving everything to the Commission. But I lost everything to THIS one. I need you to step in, for I fear I won''t be able to keep my cool. (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66826,'en','Yodeling in the Forest','Hunt all target monsters','The Ancient Forest is a living maze, so it''s not every day we see this many monsters duking it out. This could be a huge boon to our research, so suit up and head out!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66827,'en','Heavy Metal in the Waste','Hunt all target monsters','The Wildspire is a vast stretch of land, so it''s not every day we see this many monsters duking it out. This could be a huge boon to our research, so suit up and head out!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66833,'en','The Eternal Gold Rush','Slay Kulve Taroth','The mother goddess has reappeared. This time, our objective is to slay her. Get the quest from your handler or the quest board. Stand tall against her fury and return safely!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66828,'en','Symphony of the Coral','Hunt all target monsters','The Coral Highlands is relatively peaceful, so it''s not every day we see this many monsters duking it out. This could be a huge boon to our research, so suit up and head out!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66829,'en','Rotten Canzone','Hunt all target monsters','The monsters in the Rotten Vale are usually combative, but today they''re especially irritated. This could be a huge boon to our research, so suit up and head out!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66830,'en','Alt Rock Recess','Hunt all target monsters','The monsters in the Elder''s Recess are used to hanging tough, but today they''re especially irritated. This could be a huge boon to our research, so suit up and head out!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66831,'en','Ballad of the Hoarfrost','Hunt all target monsters','The monsters of the Reach tend to keep to themselves, but today they''re at each other''s throats! This could be a huge boon to our research, so suit up and head out!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66835,'en','The Wrath of Thunder Descends','Hunt a Zinogre','They say lightning never strikes the same place twice, but I wouldn''t take my chances here! Get through this in one piece and you''ll get your fill of decorations! (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(66836,'en','Ode to the Destruction','Slay a Ruiner Nergigante','Scouts have sighted an unusually fierce Ruiner Nergigante out in the field. We need you to investigate. Expect some Great Spiritvein Gems as a reward for your trouble. (Bonus HR/MR points rewarded upon completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67805,'en','Don''t Forget The Earplugs!','Hunt a Yian Garuga','An awfully big Shepherd Hare is inside the arena. Looks a bit different from the usual variety, but no mistaking it''s a Shepherd Hare with those ears! You wanna take a look and get some INSPIRATION too!? (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67806,'en','Monkey Business','Hunt a Furious Rajang','I just spotted a gigantic Goldspring Macaque! No, seriously! The way it roars into the sky and that electric golden fur, there''s no mistaking it! It''s going to be my source of INSPIRATION! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67807,'en','The Naked Truth','Slay a Shara Ishvalda','I''ve suddenly reached enlightenment. I now know the truth! All life cannot attain their true potential unless they take the same form as when they came into this world. And that means...INSPIRATION! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67808,'en','Tears from Nirvana','Slay a Blackveil Vaal Hazak','When people travel to the other side, there are places full of fear and sadness that you must bear alone. You''ll know that same feeling if you face a Blackveil Vaal Hazak. (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67809,'en','A Farewell to Zinogre','Hunt a Zinogre','The most hunted monster ever, how wonderful! Let me throw you hunters a curveball and offer a slightly different Zinogre! Those shiny things on the ground may look tempting, but be careful not to get a paw to the face!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67810,'en','Brand New Brute','Hunt a Brute Tigrex','Whoa, no wonder this Brute Tigrex''s so clean, it''s the least hunted monster! Is it crying tears of joy? Wait, those tears look a lot like armor spheres...hmm. Odd. (You cannot obtain monster materials from this quest)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67811,'en','Mew are Number One!','Hunt a Furious Rajang','Meow, child, we all know that you are the Commission''s number one hunter. The only thing you''re missing is a golden trophy, so I''ve gone and fixed up a quest for you to go out and get one. I even threw in a few goodies too. Be back in time fur dinner, meow!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67812,'en','The Evening Star','Slay an Alatreon','Alatreon has been sighted in the Secluded Valley. It seethes, like a burning star that revels in the darkness. But it''s time for the Commission to let the world know of this blazing black abomination!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67813,'en','Dawn of the Death Star','Slay an Alatreon','Alatreon has been sighted in the Secluded Valley. It screams, like an icy dead star that rejects the light. But it''s time for the Commission to let the world know of this blazing black abomination!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67814,'en','In the Tempest''s Wake','Slay a Kushala Daora','When I was a young girl, a Kushala Daora passed by our village. We hid in our homes, afraid of what tragedy it might leave in its wake. And now it''s here... May this Sealed Feystone be incentive enough for you to put a stop to this tempest.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67815,'en','Day of Ruin','Slay a Teostra','A blazing sun in a sunless land—I guess every life burns as brightly as it can, no matter where it finds itself. Just like we did those forty years ago... Anyway, I''ve prepared a Sealed Feystone for after you''ve laid this sun to rest.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67816,'en','The Cold Never Bothered Me','Slay a Lunastra','We''ve driven the "Blue Flame" into the cold prison of the supply cache, but now it seems to burn brighter than ever in its defiance. Extinguish it before it burns us all, and I''ll reward your efforts with a Sealed Feystone.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67817,'en','The Distant Dark Tide','Slay a Namielle','My mother used to lead a hunting party and told me once of a story where pleasant weather turned to violent storms, forcing the party back and spoiling a fine expedition. Perhaps the cause was Namielle. I hope your hunt divulges some answers...');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67818,'en','The Last White Knight','Hunt a Frostfang Barioth','We''ve finally found it! The tree top assassin that controls the frost. "The Last White Knight", they call it. Outmuscling it is out of the question. No, only the most devoted can topple this beast. I await your report, Hunter.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67819,'en','The Place Where Winter Sleeps','Slay a Velkhana','As leader of this hunt, I''ve been granted authority to add new recruits to our ranks. Our target is an incredibly ferocious Velkhana. Want a challenge? Then help us send it to its end!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67820,'en','Fade to Black','Slay Fatalis','We''ve been tasked with slaying Fatalis, a monster known only in legends handed-down. This beast will test all of your limits, but I know you''ll be ready.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(61809,'en','Paolumu Lullabies','Hunt a Nightshade Paolumu','The Admiral and Chef managed to capture a Nightshade Paolumu, but something seemed pawfully off. I didn''t mention anything to those two, but purrhaps you could take a look, Meowster?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(64801,'en','Balloon Fight','Hunt all target monsters','OK. I, uh, admit that I went a little crazy with the party prep, but I swear I did NOT blow up those balloons. Pop those pests and the Second Fleet Master will hook you up with armor spheres!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(64802,'en','Talk About a Party Foul...','Hunt a Seething Bazelgeuse','Wooo, that was one GNARLY party! But some, uh, party pooper left all his party poop all over the place... Sorry, Player. Someone''s gotta clean up this mess and it ain''t me! But if you do, the Second Fleet Master will hook you up with some sweet armor spheres!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67101,'en','The Proving','Hunt an Anjanath','We''ve waited so long for this day. It''s time for you to participate in the Proving and become a true brave. Offer your trophy to the All-Mother, and you shall be blessed generously.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67102,'en','Lessons of the Wild','Slay 8 Barnos','It''s time for some special training. Wingdrakes are feeble things compared to larger monsters, but even they can take down a hunter. Cull their numbers and we''ll prep some new Palico gear.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67607,'en','The Heart of the Nora','Hunt 2 Deviljho','No...Mother''s Heart! The survivors hiding inside the mountain will be buried if you don''t take down those monsters. Overcome this threat and I will provide you with special equipment!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3171,'en','Arena Master Quest 01','Slay a Banbaro','In the monster corner: Banbaro, the Ruler of the Reach, the Champ of Tramp! If you can''t dig your own grave, he''ll dig it for you! You ready to duke it out with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3071,'en','Arena Master Quest 02','Slay a Nightshade Paolumu','In the monster corner: Nightshade Paolumu, the Sultan of Slumber, the Flightmare! Get caught in the sleeper hold, and it''s lights out! You ready to duke it out with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3072,'en','Arena Master Quest 03','Slay a Nargacuga','In the monster corner: Nargacuga, the Shadowy Slayer, the Nimble Ninja! If you can''t see him, it''s already too late! You ready to duke it out with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3073,'en','Arena Master Quest 04','Slay an Acidic Glavenus','In the monster corner: Acidic Glavenus, the Colonel of Corrosion, The Dino Dueler! There''s no stoppin'' once he gets to choppin''! You ready to duke it out with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3074,'en','Arena Master Quest 05','Slay all target monsters','In the monster corner: An Odogaron-Ebony Odogaron tag team! The hounds are out, and you''re about to get woofed! You ready to duke it out with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3091,'en','Arena Master Quest 06','Slay a Zinogre','In the monster corner: Zinogre, the Bug Zapper, the Thunder Clapper! When this pup gets to howlin'', better throw the towel in! You ready to duke it out with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(3092,'en','Arena Master Quest 07','Slay all target monsters','In the monster corner: A Tigrex-Brute Tigrex tag team! Don''t get between these two, unless you wanna be a wishbone! You ready to duke it out with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63071,'en','Challenge Quest 1: MR Intermediate','Slay all target monsters','In the monster corner: A Tobi-Kadachi-Viper Tobi-Kadachi tag team! Stay on your toes against this tandem because the fur is about to fly! You ready to duke it out with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63072,'en','Challenge Quest 2: MR Intermediate','Slay all target monsters','In the monster corner: An Anjanath-Fulgur Anjanath tag...team...? Bless their hearts, I think their lil'' ol'' arms are too short to tag... You ready to duke it out with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63073,'en','Challenge Quest 1: MR Expert','Slay a Yian Garuga','In the monster corner: Yian Garuga, the Screamin'' Demon, the Beaked Berzerker! You''ve never seen crazy like this before! You ready to duke it out with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(63074,'en','Challenge Quest 2: MR Expert','Slay a Savage Deviljho','In the monster corner: Deviljho, the food chain dominator, the pulverizing pickle! This is one hoss that likes to throw its weight around! You ready to duke it out with set weapons and armor?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67822,'en','A Fish to Whet Your Appetite','Deliver 2 Great Whetfish','Not only are those big boys sharp to a fault, if you can haul them here fresh as a daisy, they might be useful as a weapon too! So get on out there and snag some, will ya? (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67823,'en','Fetching Light Pearls','Deliver 8 Light Pearls','I saw those Kelbi eyes glow like a pearl in the dark! Then it struck me. Yes, INSPIRATION! To the message boards! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67824,'en','To Our World','Slay a Rathalos','Why is that thing still alive? I thought we killed it! Does that mean I''m in the...? At any rate, I need to find a way back to my world. In this quest, you will get to play as Artemis.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67825,'en','The New World','Head to Area 8','Looks like I''m back in this world again, but where are those two? Guess I better look for them... In this quest, you will get to play as Artemis.');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67826,'en','Skyward Snipers','Deliver 5 Grandfather Mantagrells','You''ve seen those big Grandfather Mantagrells being all floaty in the air, right? My notes say they''re especially weak to sudden shocks. I bet if you use your slinger you can get one for me to play with—I mean study, of course! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67827,'en','Camoflawed','Hunt a Rathian','The young miss I work with needs to research some critter in a Rath nest and almost went wearin'' an herbivore disguise. Good thing I stopped her before she got swooped up. Could you go hunt that Rathian so she can get her critter fix? (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67828,'en','Kadachi Twins','Hunt all target monsters','It''s so freakin'' cold out here that I came up with a design for some warm armor based on a monster! It looks strong, yes, strong indeed! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67829,'en','Seeing is Believing','Hunt a Tigrex','Yo, Scrawny. This hungover hunter came by sayin'' he''s seein'' things in the Arena. He was so shook up about it that it''s made him quit drinkin''. Go check it out for him, will ya? (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67830,'en','The True Tyrant','Slay a Tigrex','We salute all hunters who have conquered the New World using everything at their disposal. Embark on this quest that will challenge you and may the Sapphire Star light your way!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67831,'en','The Assassin','Hunt a Nargacuga','I dreamt of a man with the grace of an assassin...and ever since, I''ve been going bonkers thinking about what I want to work on next. Ya gotta help me out here! (Upgrades the Assassin''s Hood upon first completion.)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67832,'en','USJ: Shine On Forever','Slay a Velkhana','Special delivery from USJ to you: the perfect stage for you to sparkle with a monster that truly shines! May the shine never end! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67833,'en','The Conqueror of Hoarfrost','Slay all target monsters','We salute all hunters who have conquered the New World using everything at their disposal. Embark on this quest that will challenge you and may the Sapphire Star light your way!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67834,'en','A Star That Will Never Dim','Slay a Namielle','We salute all hunters who have conquered the New World using everything at their disposal. Embark on this quest that will challenge you and may the Sapphire Star light your way!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67835,'en','Wearer of the Iceborne Crown','Slay a Velkhana','We salute all hunters who have conquered the New World using everything at their disposal. Embark on this quest that will challenge you and may the Sapphire Star light your way!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67836,'en','USJ: Ballet of Frost','Hunt a Frostfang Barioth','Special delivery from USJ to you: the perfect stage for you to duel with a monster with fangs of frost! May the excitement never end! (Special material rewards)');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67837,'en','Aiming for the Light','Slay a Namielle','We salute all hunters who have conquered the New World using everything at their disposal. Embark on this quest that will challenge you and may the Sapphire Star light your way!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67838,'en','All That Glitters is Furious','Hunt a Furious Rajang','We know of the Furious Rajang, but only just that. Do you know why? Because when it spots you, it''s already over. Can our Sapphire Star stand up to the golden fury?');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67839,'en','Fear No Scars','Slay a Scarred Yian Garuga','We salute all hunters who have conquered the New World using everything at their disposal. Embark on this quest that will challenge you and may the Sapphire Star light your way!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67840,'en','Power and Technique','Slay all target monsters','We salute all hunters who have conquered the New World using everything at their disposal. Embark on this quest that will challenge you and may the Sapphire Star light your way!');
INSERT INTO quest_text VALUES(67841,'en','Achy Brachy Heart','Slay a Raging Brachydios','My senior hunting friend went off to slay a Raging Brachydios once, and when I asked about it she just said, "I just don''t think you''d understand." Can you believe that? I almost blew up at her! Now I have to go see it for myself.');
